\p  
\v 8 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ eŇčken…õ fum p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ …Ēy…Ē akata Ňča p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf pap…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 PoloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē anc…Ēf doco, pan…õk…ôt d…ôkar…Ēr…Ē k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti d…ôdap m…Ē, w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ eŇčkek…ôr…õ pi p…ôc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, …Ēy…Ē pi.  
\v 10 PoloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn mp…õ o mp…õ p'an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ powos, yuruya ya Aruna f…ôp Ňč…Ē aŇčyer pi p…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ Ňča gb…õp. 
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu 
\p  
\v 11 Sariy…õ ns…õ s…ôc…ôm…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu dar…ôŇč, nk…õ aŇčken…õ MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē fum …õndeken…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôyif MARIKI barka teta p…ôt…Ēt p…Ēn-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôdeŇč…ôr poloŇčn…õ pa c…ôcom c…ôlok-lok nc…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro ma olif m…Ē ta k…ôy…Ē lebin, k…Ē biskit b…Ēt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin pasop…ôt bi moro ma olif, k…Ē c…ôcom c…ôlok-lok nc…õ alomps…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ moro ma olif m…Ē.  
\v 13 P…ôkek…ôr…õ s…Ē c…ôcom c…ôlok-lok nc…õ an…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin m…Ē, k…ôdeŇč…ôr ka k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôyif MARIKI barka k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu k…Ēn.  
\v 14 W…ôkayi p…ôbeli p…ôken…õ MARIKI pipic d…ôyoloŇčn…õ y…Ēn f…ôp, y…õlp…ôs yay…Ēk…Ē ya w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ …õw…õs…ôs…ôr mecir ma p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ pa k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu d…ôtetek m…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ē yi.  
\v 15 S…õm ya p…Ēc…Ēl pa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôyif MARIKI barka k…Ē ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ aŇčloŇčn…õ pi m…Ē, id…Ē aŇčs…Ēm yi ali pin af…Ēsak pedir…õ haŇč b…ôtb…ôt. 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē w…ôkayi eŇčkek…ôr…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôd…õr…ôm, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpoc…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs-…õ, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ endekek…ôr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, id…Ē aŇčs…Ēm pi. K'asak p…õlp…ôs pedir…õ-…õ, antam k…ôs…Ēm pi d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 17 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a s…õm y…õntamb…ôr afum pasak yi yedir…õ s…Ē-…õ, d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da maas pac…Ēf yi.  
\v 18 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēs…Ēm s…õm ya k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôpaŇčn…õ ka p…ôforu kaŇčk…Ē tataka ta maas, fum nw…õ eŇčken…õ MARIKI poloŇčn…õ m…Ē, MARIKI …Ēf…ĒbaŇč pi, k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ēn kaŇčk…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ k…Ē daka o daka, s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē oŇč y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk. Nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčs…Ēm yi m…Ē, …õsar…õ kiciya.  
\v 19 K…Ē paka p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk poŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē-…õ, ta pas…Ēm yi, pagbal yi d…ôn…õnc. M…õn…õ fum p…ôs…Ēk a p…ôctam k…ôs…Ēm s…õm ya k…ôloŇčn…õ kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 20 Mba fum nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēs…Ēm s…õm ya k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka MARIKI ta …Ēs…Ēk-…õ, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aYisrayel dac…Ē.  
\v 21 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ ogbuŇč…õn…õ paka p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk, p…ôm…Ē fum w…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, s…õm y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk, yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk, paka p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk mp…õ o mp…õ, a w…ôkayi p…ôs…Ēm s…õm ya k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka MARIKI m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aYisrayel dac…Ē. 
\s1 Sariy…õ s…ôl…Ēma ns…õ s…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčandec…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 23 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p Ta Ňčadi moro ma wana, ma aŇčkesiya k…Ē ma wir.  
\v 24 Moro ma w…õs…õm nw…õ ant…Ēfay k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…õs…õm nw…õ s…õm yendif m…Ē, n…ôntam mi k…ôy…Ēn…õ mes f…ôp, mba ta n…ôdi mi.  
\v 25 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ edi moro ma p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ mp…õ aŇčkek…ôr…õ pac…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.  
\v 26 Ta n…ômun mecir, m…Ēy…Ēn…õ ma ab…õmp, ma p…Ēc…Ēl k…ôfo nk…õ o nk…õ n…ôŇčyi m…Ē.  
\v 27 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ omun mecir m…Ēy…Ēn…õ mm…õ o mm…õ m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 28 K…Ē MARIKI osom s…Ē Musa:  
\v 29 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: M…ôna nw…õ m…ôndeken…õ MARIKI poloŇčn…õ teta k…ôpaŇčn…õ ka p…ôforu m…Ē, m…ôken…õ k…Ē f…ôk…ôl y…Ēn ny…õ w…ôkayi embel…ôr poloŇčn…õ p…Ēn pa k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu dac…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 30 Fum nw…õ eŇčken…õ MARIKI poloŇčn…õ m…Ē, p…ôkek…ôr…õ moro ma p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, p…ôkek…ôr…õ mi k…Ē k…ômp…ôcp…ôc nk…õ antubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē.  
\v 31 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôc…Ēf…õ MARIKI moro mam…Ēk…Ē nde tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč, mba k…ômp…ôcp…ôc k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka Aruna k'awut …Ēn arkun.  
\v 32 D…ôyoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu n…ômbel…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ al…ôŇčk Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 33 Awut arkun a Aruna dac…Ē, nw…õ eŇčkek…ôr…õ mecir k…Ē moro ma p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ pa k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu m…Ē, nk…Ēn …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē al…ôŇčk ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 34 IŇčl…õk d…ôyoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu ny…õ aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ ina MARIKI m…Ē: K…ômp…ôcp…ôc nk…õ antubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč em m…Ē, k'al…ôŇčk nŇč…õ aŇčwur…õ m…Ē, is…ĒŇč yi Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn. S…õm yay…Ēk…Ē yende y…Ēcy…Ēn…õ yaŇčan, sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē tendey…Ēn…õ nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 35 F…ôk…ôl yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē ambel…õ Aruna k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn d…ôyoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ and…ôs Ňča dekiriŇč k…ôy…Ēn…õ aloŇčn…õ a MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 36 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē MARIKI osom aka Yisrayel k…ôde k…ôcs…ĒŇč aloŇčn…õ f…ôk…ôl yay…Ēk…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ amb…Ēy Ňča m…Ē, sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē tendey…Ēn…õ Ňča d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp daŇčan. 
\p  
\v 37 Sariy…õ sa yoloŇčn…õ s…Ē saŇčs…õ: Sariy…õ sa y…Ēc…Ēl yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, sa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn, sa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, sa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya, sa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôd…ôs ka dekiriŇč da aloŇčn…õ k…Ē sa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu.  
\v 38 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa d…ôndo d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …õnaloku aka Yisrayel k…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 8  
\ms2 AloŇčn…õ ac…Ēk…Ēc…Ēk…Ē 
\mr 8-10 
\s1 K…ôpus k…Ē k…ôd…ôs ka aloŇčn…õ dekiriŇč 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôl…õk Aruna k'awut …Ēn arkun, yamos ya aloŇčn…õ, moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus…õ, tura ta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, Ňčkesiya yorkun ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôfala ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin.  
\v 3 M…ôloŇčka aka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ d'aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Musa …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaloŇčkan…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ d'aŇčgbancan. 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē Musa oloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom aka Yisrayel k…ôy…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Musa …Ēnc…ĒŇč Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun, k'embik…õn…õn…õ Ňča domun.  
\v 7 K'…õmb…õr Aruna duma dedisr…õ k'…õŇčgb…ônc k…Ē tabataba, k'endeŇč…ôr k…Ē burumus k…Ē duma da ef…Ēd nd…õ …õnagb…ônc…õ tabataba pa duma da ef…Ēd nd…õ …õnakot k…Ē tadar…ôŇč m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē Musa …õŇčgb…õk k…Ē yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ ny…õ …õnab…õr masar m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ m…Ē: Tasar ta \it Yurim \it*k…Ē ta \it Tumim\it*.  
\v 9 K'…õnc…ôp k…Ē k…ôfak…ôl, k'…õnd…õt…ôr ki tekiriŇč ab…Ēp…ôr Ňča k…õma, t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta d…ôKanu, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus…õ, k'…Ēmb…Ēy d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē ca c…ôk…Ē y…õnayi di m…Ē, k'ompus yi f…ôp.  
\v 11 K'…õw…õs…ôs…ôr moro tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu haŇč cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč teta k…ôpus ka pi, k'…Ēmb…Ēy tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di f…ôp, k…ôsamp k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôpus yi m…Ē.  
\v 12 K'oloŇč…ôr domp da Aruna moro mam…Ēk…Ē, k'…Ēmb…Ēy Aruna s…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôpus k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 13 K…Ē Musa …Ēnc…ĒŇč…õn…õ awut arkun a Aruna, k'…õmb…õr Ňča suma s…ôdisr…õ. K'…õŇčgb…ônc…ôs Ňča mabamaba, k'…õnc…ôp…ôs Ňča c…ôfak…ôl p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Musa …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ tura toloŇčn…õ ta kiciya. Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčandeŇč…ôr pi waca d…ôromp.  
\v 15 K…Ē Musa …õfay pi, k'asu t…Ēb…Ēl k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ pi disr…õ. K…Ē Musa …õl…õk…õ mecir t…õl…ôr t…Ēn k'osop…ôt mi l…õn maŇčk…ôl…õ ya moŇčkubut ma tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu teta k…ôpus…õ ka pi MARIKI. Tat…Ēk…Ē t'…õnas…Ēk…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu. K'oloŇč…ôr mecir m…õlp…ôs m…Ēk…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa tetek toloŇčn…õ, k'ompus pi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka pi k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk moro m…Ēk…Ē m…õnakump yedisr…õ m…Ē f…ôp, p…ôwotwot…ôr pa mim k…Ē fi ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē moro ma yi, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.  
\v 17 Mba k…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…Ēf nde saŇčka todoru y…õlp…ôs ya tura: Akata, s…õm k…Ē yedisr…õ ya aputuk p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē Musa …õŇčk…õr…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf. Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčandeŇč…ôr Ňči waca d…ôromp.  
\v 19 K…Ē Musa …õfay Ňči, k'asu t…Ēb…Ēl, k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ pi disr…õ. K…Ē Musa …õw…õs…ôs…ôr mi tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu c…ôs…ôk haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.  
\v 20 K…Ē Musa …õnc…õn…ôs aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē f…ôk…ôl f…ôk…ôl. K'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI k…ôy…õf…õ domp, f…ôk…ôl, k…Ē moro ma aŇčkesiya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 21 K'…õyak…õ yedisr…õ k…Ē w…õc…ôk domun, a k'endec…Ēf yi f…ôp nde tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu k…ôroŇč. AŇčkesiya Ňčorkun ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē f…ôp Ňč…Ē Musa …õnac…Ēf…õ MARIKI. PoloŇčn…õ pap…Ēk…Ē p'anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI, amb…Ēnc Ňča pi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc. Musa …õnay…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē Musa …õŇčk…õr…õ aŇčkesiya Ňča m…õr…ôŇč nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôd…ôs ka dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē. Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčandeŇč…ôr aŇčkesiya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē waca d…ôromp.  
\v 23 K…Ē Musa …õfay Ňči, k'asu t…Ēb…Ēl, k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ pi disr…õ. K…Ē Musa …õl…õk mecir, k'osop mi al…ôŇč…ôs Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka Aruna k…Ē t…õl…ôr t…Ēn t…Ēp…ĒŇč ta k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē t…õl…ôr t…Ēn t…Ēp…ĒŇč pa k…ôc…ôk k…Ēn k…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 24 K…Ē Musa …Ēnc…ĒŇč…õn…õ awut arkun a Aruna, k'osop Ňča mecir mam…Ēk…Ē nde l…ôŇč…ôs yaŇčan ya k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, m…õl…ôr maŇčan m…Ēp…ĒŇč ma waca waŇčan w…Ēt…Ēt k…Ē m…õl…ôr maŇčan m…Ēp…ĒŇč ma w…õc…ôk waŇčan w…Ēt…Ēt, k…Ē Musa …õw…õs…ôs…ôr mecir m…õlp…ôs m…Ēk…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu c…ôs…ôk haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.  
\v 25 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk k…ôleŇča k…Ē moro m…Ēk…Ē m…õnakump yedisr…õ ya aŇčkesiya ny…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôwotwot…ôr pa mim k…Ē fi m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē moro ma yi k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňča k…ôc…ôk k…ôt…Ēt. 
\p  
\v 26 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk k…ôfala ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin nk…õ anac…ômb…ôr MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, k'…õl…õk k…ôcom k…ôlok-lok kin, k…ôcom k…ôlok-lok kin nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ moro ma olif m…Ē, k…Ē biskit, k'endeŇč…ôr yi moro ma p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…ôroŇč.  
\v 27 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk yi f…ôp k'…õmb…õr Aruna d…ôwaca k…Ē awut …Ēn, k'ontubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 28 K…Ē Musa …õmbaŇč…ôr Ňča yi d…ôwaca, k'endeŇč yi p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf k…ôroŇč, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi f…ôp MARIKI d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôd…ôs ka aloŇčn…õ dekiriŇč da y…õb…ôc ya d…ôKanu. K…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē, nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, nk…õ amb…Ēnc Ňča ki Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 29 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk k…ômp…ôcp…ôc ka aŇčkesiya ŇčoloŇčn…õn…õ Ňča k…ôd…ôs dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ, k'ontubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňči MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča Musa, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.  
\v 30 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus…õ k…Ē mecir m…Ēk…Ē m…õnayi nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu k…ôroŇč m…Ē, k'…õw…õs…ôs…ôr mi Aruna k…Ē yamos y…Ēn, awut …Ēn k…Ē yamos yaŇčan. K'ompus Aruna k…Ē yamos y…Ēn, awut a Aruna arkun k…Ē yamos yaŇčan. 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun: ¬ęN…ôp…õc s…õm ny…õ nde kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, dif…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēs…Ēm yi k…Ē c…ôcom nc…õ c…ôyi nn…Ē k…ôfala ka k…ôd…ôs ka dekiriŇč m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē inaluks…õ nu k…ôsom ka Kanu m…Ē: Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn ŇčaŇčs…Ēm yi.  
\v 32 K…Ē y…Ēnt…Ēlip-…õ, n…ôc…Ēf y…õlp…ôs ya s…õm k…Ē c…ôcom cac…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 33 Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč n…ôf…Ēy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu haŇč mataka ma k…ôd…ôs konu dekiriŇč mecep…ôr, bawo mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m'and…ôs nu dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ.  
\v 34 Tant…õ teyi m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, t…Ē MARIKI nk…Ēn w…ôs…ôrka osom a pay…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu m…Ē.  
\v 35 Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē n…ôndeyi d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, pibi k…Ē daŇč k…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sa MARIKI saŇčs…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ôfi m…Ē: Tant…õ t'anasom im.¬Ľ  
\v 36 Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčay…Ē m…Ēy…Ē f…ôp mm…õ MARIKI …õnasom Musa nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē. 
\c 9  
\s1 YoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya Aruna k'awut …Ēn nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu 
\p  
\v 1 Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas k…Ē Musa ewe Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka abeki aka Yisrayel.  
\v 2 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôl…õk tura t…õf…õt ta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin teta poloŇčn…õ mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, m…õr…ôŇč ma yi f…ôp ta y…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp, m…ôment…ôr yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 3 M…ôloku aka Yisrayel nt…õ: N…ôl…õk ambiyofo teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, tura ta teren tin k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin ta y…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp, n…ôc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI,  
\v 4 tura tin k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin Ňča k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paloŇčn…õ yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro ma olif m…Ē, bawo MARIKI endewur…ôr nu m…Ēk…Ē!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 5 K'aŇčkek…ôr…õ ca y…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnasom k…ôkek…ôr…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē. K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčab…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 6 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom, n…ôy…Ē ti nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…Ēr…Ē da delel da MARIKI dowur…ôr nu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu. M…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya kam k…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf pam, m…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ kiciya kam k…Ē ka afum. M…ôs…ĒŇč s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya afum, m…ôtubucn…õ s…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom ti m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Aruna …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu k'…õfay tura t…õf…õt teta kiciya ka nk…Ēns…ôrka. K'asu t…Ēb…Ēl, k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ pi disr…õ.  
\v 9 K…Ē awut arkun a Aruna ŇčaŇčken…õ k…Ē mi. K'Aruna …õŇčgb…ôt mi t…õl…ôr t…Ēn k'osop…ôt l…õn maŇčk…ôl…õ ya moŇčkubut ma tetek toloŇčn…õ, k'oloŇč…ôr m…õlp…ôs p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa pi.  
\v 10 K'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč moro ma p…Ēc…Ēl, fi m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē p…ôwot-wot…ôr pa mim ma k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.  
\v 11 Mba k'aŇčk…Ē pac…Ēf saŇčka tadar…ôŇč s…õm k…Ē akata. 
\p  
\v 12 K'Aruna …õfay p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, k'asu t…Ēb…Ēl, k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ pi disr…õ. K…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē, k'…õw…õs…ôs…ôr mi c…ôs…ôk ca tetek toloŇčn…õ haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.  
\v 13 K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē f…ôk…ôl k…Ē domp da poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.  
\v 14 K'…õyak yedisr…õ ya p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…õc…ôk, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč k…Ē poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf. 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē Aruna oloŇčn…õ yoloŇčn…õ ya aka Yisrayel. K'…õl…õk ambiyofo nŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanak…õr…õ k…ôdeloŇčn…õ teta kiciya m…Ē, k'…õfay Ňči, k'oloŇčn…õ Ňči teta kiciya p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloŇčn…õ tura m…Ē.  
\v 16 K'eŇčken…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē.  
\v 17 K'eŇčkek…ôr…õ yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ny…õ …õnalas d…ôk…ôca m…Ē, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf p…õb…ôtb…ôt.  
\v 18 K'…õfay tura k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu ka afum. K'asu t…Ēb…Ēl, k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ pi disr…õ. K…Ē awut arkun a Aruna Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē mecir mam…Ēk…Ē, k'…õw…õs…ôs…ôr mi c…ôs…ôk ca tetek toloŇčn…õ haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.  
\v 19 K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē moro ma tura k…Ē aŇčkesiya, k…ôleŇča k…Ē moro moŇčkump fi k…Ē p…ôwot-wot…ôr pa mim.  
\v 20 K'endeŇč moro d…ôk…ômp…ôcp…ôc, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ MARIKI moro d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.  
\v 21 K…Ē Aruna ontubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč k…ômp…ôcp…ôc k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnasom ti m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē Aruna eyekti waca darenc nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, k'ontolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt. Nt…õ elip k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, k…ôloŇčn…õ ka poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu m…Ē, k'ontor tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu.  
\v 23 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčamb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ. Nt…õ Ňčandewur m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt. K…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI dowur…ôr aka Yisrayel f…ôp.  
\v 24 K…Ē n…õnc dowur MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč k…Ē d…Ēnc…Ēf p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē moro ma pi d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč. K…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčan…ôŇčk ti. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkul-kul…õn…õ p…ôbotu, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôp mobu d…ônt…Ēf. 
\c 10  
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôbal 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē awut arkun m…õr…ôŇč a Aruna, Nadab k…Ē Abihu nw…õ o nw…õ k'…õl…õk tap k'…õmb…õr pi n…õnc disr…õ k'…Ēnc…Ēl…ôr suray. K…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õ MARIKI n…õnc nd…õ d…õnat…Ētes…õ nd…õ …õnat…Ēsom Ňča k…ôk…õr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē n…õnc dowur MARIKI tekiriŇč, k…Ē d…Ēnc…Ēf Ňča, k…Ē Ňčafi m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 3 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI …õnasom: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻIfaŇč aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčl…Ēt…ôrn'em m…Ē, 
\q1 Ňčac…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka kance, 
\q1 Ňčade Ňčaclel…ôs dosoku dem. 
\q1 Ňäacyek-yek…ôs n…Ēr…Ē da debeki dem 
\q1 aka Yisrayel f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\m K…Ē Aruna …õncaŇčk pem. 
\p  
\v 4 K…Ē Musa ewe Misay…õl k…Ē ElcafaŇč awut a Usiy…õl papa ka Aruna w…ôf…õt, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ n…ôde n…ôl…õk aw…õnc nu aŇča, n…ôwur…õn…õ Ňča daŇčgbancan Ňčosoku, n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ Ňča saŇčka.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K'akak…Ē Ňčanc…ĒŇčn…õ k…Ē Ňčal…õk c…ôbel c…ôŇčan Ňčas…Ēr…Ēb…õrn…õ suma s…ôdisr…õ s…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ Ňča d…ôsaŇčka, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku ti m…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna, Elasar k…Ē Itamar, awut a Aruna: ¬ęTa n…ôsakti c…ôfon conu. Ta n…ôwal-wali yamos yonu, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôt…Ēfi, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôt…Ēk…õr…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel m…õt…õl…õ. Aw…õnc nu aŇča, aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčabok teta afum aŇč…õ n…õnc da MARIKI dendif m…Ē.  
\v 7 Ta n…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, ta tedes…ĒŇč'on k…ôfi, bawo moro m…Ēb…Ēy teta k…ôpus ma MARIKI meyi nu d…ôris.¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē. 
\s1 Sariy…õ sa yomun yecis…ôs 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Aruna:  
\v 9 ¬ęM…ôna k…Ē awut am: K…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôcb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu-…õ, ta n…ômun w…õn, ta n…ômun s…Ē maŇčk…Ēnt…Ē mm…õ o mm…õ, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôt…Ēfi. Tende t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu sariy…õ sa doru o doru, d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp donu.  
\v 10 Ti tendes…ĒŇč'on n…ôctam k…ôgb…õy paka popus k…Ē p…Ēt…Ēpus, paka posoku k…Ē p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 11 N…ôctam s…Ē k…ôt…ôks…õ aka Yisrayel sariy…õ ns…õ MARIKI …õnasom Musa k…ôdeloku Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…Ēs…Ēt…Ē pa aloŇčn…õ yoloŇčn…õ dac…Ē 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna, k…Ē awut …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē m…Ē, Elasar k…Ē Itamar: ¬ęN…ôl…õk yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn y…õlp…ôs ya yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, n…ôdi yi tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôs…ôk. Ta n…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl yi lebin de, yeri yosoku y…Ē ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 13 N…ôdi yi k…ôfo k…ôsoku: It…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku nu m…ôna k…Ē awut am arkun teta yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, it…Ē anasom im.  
\v 14 N…ôs…Ēm s…Ē yi k…ôfo k…ôsoku, m…ôna k…Ē awut am k…ôy…õf…õ k…ômp…ôcp…ôc nk…õ anatubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč MARIKI k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňč…Ēk…Ē anabel…ôr m…Ē. As…ĒŇč nu yi, k…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku a m…ôn'…Ēy…Ē yi k'awut am, nn…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu ya aka Yisrayel yeyi m…Ē.  
\v 15 Aka Yisrayel Ňčade Ňčack…õr…õ moro ma y…Ēc…Ēl yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ ande pacc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, Ňčabel…ôr al…ôŇčk k…Ē k…ômp…ôcp…ôc Ňčatubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč. K'alip ti-…õ, al…ôŇčk k…Ē k…ômp…ôcp…ôc y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yonu, bawo sariy…õ sa MARIKI s…Ē, s…õm yonu y…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē doru o doru, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom ti m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē Musa …õnt…õn ambiyofo ŇčoloŇčn…õn…õ kiciya belbel, mba k'…Ēnk…Ē p…ôb…ôp pac…Ēf Ňči. K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Musa nn…Ē Elasar k…Ē Itamar Ňčayi m…Ē, awut arkun a Aruna aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Musa eyif Ňča:  
\v 17 ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…Ēs…Ēm…õ ambiyofo ŇčoloŇčn…õn…õ kiciya nde k…ôfo k…ôsoku-…õ? Yeri yosoku y…Ē ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, …Ēs…ĒŇč nu yi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôcsar…õ kiciya ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel, n…ôctubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan m…Ē, it…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nu Ňči.  
\v 18 Anakek…ôr…õ f…õ mecir mam…Ēk…Ē nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku disr…õ. P…ônamar n…ôs…Ēm ambiyofo ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē nde k…ôfo k…ôpus m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē inasom nu ti m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Aruna oloku Musa: ¬ęD…Ēs…Ēk dand…õ d…Ē awut em Ňčanakek…ôr…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya k…ôŇčan k…Ē ka poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč. M…ônc…ôr…õ belbel t…Ēk…Ē t…õnas…Ēt'em m…Ē: K'is…Ēm d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēm…Ēk…Ē poloŇčn…õ pa kiciya-…õ, t…Ēmb…Ēt MARIKI ba?¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Musa ene ti, k…Ē t…Ēmb…Ēt k…Ē. 
\c 11  
\ms1 Ca ny…õ y…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē 
\s1 S…õm ny…õ MARIKI owos…õ nu k…ôs…Ēm k…Ē ny…õ …Ēm…Ēn…õ k…ôs…Ēm m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa k…Ē Aruna:  
\v 2 ¬ęN…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p S…õm ny…õ yeyi d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē f…ôp, ny…õ y'awos…õ nu k…ôde k…ôcs…Ēm:  
\v 3 N…ôndetam k…ôcs…Ēm s…õm f…ôp ny…õ y…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ m…õl…ôr m…Ē, y…õcnak…ômn…õ k…Ē y…Ēnt…Ēyi k…ôs…Ēm…ôt-…õ, p…ôm…Ē wana.  
\v 4 Mba ta n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm s…õm ny…õ y…õŇčnak…ômn…õ gb…ôc…ôr…ôm ta y…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ m…õl…ôr m…Ē. Ta n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm s…Ē s…õm ny…õ y…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ m…õl…ôr m…õr…ôŇč gb…ôc…ôr…ôm ta y…õnak…ômn…õ m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē s…õm ny…õ: Y…Ēk…Ēm…õ y…õŇčnak…ômn…õ, mba y…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ f…õ m…õl…ôr, y…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 5 Debem da d…ômasar s…Ē d…õŇčnak…ômn…õ, mba d…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ f…õ m…õl…ôr, d…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 6 T…Ēr…Ēp t…õŇčnak…ômn…õ, mba p…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ f…õ m…õl…ôr, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 7 As…Ēp Ňč…õŇčgb…õy…õn…õ m…õl…ôr, mba Ňč…Ēf…Ēnak…ômn…õ yeri p…ôm…Ē wana, Ňč…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 8 Ta n…ôs…Ēm s…õm ya as…Ēp, ta n…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ Ňčefi Ňča yi. Ňä…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ s…õm ny…õ yeyi d…ôromun m…Ē, ny…õ y…Ē awos…õ nu k…ôde k…ôcs…Ēm: S…õm ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē y…õŇč…õrn…õn…õ k…Ē wokwok m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē yeyi d…ôromun m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…ôc…ôba t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…ôc…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 10 Mba s…õm y…õf…õt y…õf…õt k…Ē y…Ēp…ĒŇč ny…õ yeyi d…ôromun m…Ē f…ôp, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…ôc…ôba t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…ôc…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē, yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē wokwok k…Ē y…õŇč…õrn…õn…õ m…Ē, n…ôter y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk yay…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 11 N…ôter s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē, ta n…ôs…Ēm yi. N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôcgbuŇč…õn…õ yi, n…ôl…Ēm pefi pa yi p…ôm…Ē p…ôyikyik mp…õ n…ônter m…Ē.  
\v 12 N…ôter s…õm ya d…ôromun f…ôp ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē y…õŇč…õrn…õn…õ k…Ē wokwok m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē b…õmp ny…õ y…Ē n…ôndeter, ta n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm yi, y…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē: Asiksik, ay…Ēf…ôn, asiksik Ňča d…ôk…ôba,  
\v 14 aŇčk…ôlok…ôlo, t…ôŇčgb…õ k…Ē dokom…õn…õ da yi,  
\v 15 b…õmp yaser k…Ē dokom…õn…õ da yi f…ôp,  
\v 16 ot…ôris, awump Ňča dare, ac…ôm…õc…ôm…õ, ab…ôkar k…Ē dokom…õn…õ da yi,  
\v 17 awump Ňča dop k…Ē dokom…õn…õ da Ňči, aŇčgbeŇčgb…ôlec,  
\v 18 antombon, ay…Ēf…ôn,  
\v 19 k…ôt…õp k…Ē dokom…õn…õ da yi, k…Ē tempirfin. 
\p  
\v 20 N…ôter yeyi w…ôyeŇč y…õf…õt y…õf…õt ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē banca y…õcf…õl…ôr k…Ē y…Ēck…Ēt w…õc…ôk wa yi maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē, y…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 21 Mba yoyok…õ-yok…õ y…õf…õt y…õf…õt dac…Ē ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē banca y…õcf…õl…ôr mba y…Ēck…Ēt…õn…õ s…Ē w…õc…ôk maŇčk…ôl…õ m…Ē, n…ôntam k…ôs…Ēm ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē w…õc…ôk m…õr…ôŇč nw…õ w…õntam k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ yi k…ôyok…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 22 Yoyok…õ-yok…õ ny…õ y…õŇčf…õl…ôr m…Ē, ny…õ y…Ē n…ônde n…ôctam k…ôcs…Ēm: Dokom…õn…õ da c…ôlaŇčk…ôma k…Ē c…ôcal.  
\v 23 Mba yeŇčes…ôm y…õf…õt y…õf…õt y…Ēl…Ēma ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē banca y…õcf…õl…ôr, y…Ēck…Ēt s…Ē w…õc…ôk maŇčk…ôl…õ wa yi k…ôroŇč m…Ē f…ôp, y…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē, n…ôde n…ôter yi. 
\s1 YogbuŇč…õn…õ ya s…õm ny…õ y…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē 
\p  
\v 24 S…õm ny…õ y…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk: Nw…õ o nw…õ ogbuŇč…õn…õ wefi wa yi, w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.  
\v 25 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr w…õs…õm wefi waw…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, p…ômar p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.  
\v 26 W…õs…õm nw…õ o nw…õ w…Ēnt…Ēgb…õy…õn…õ m…õl…ôr belbel k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti ta w…õŇčnak…ômn…õ k…Ē wendeŇčes…ôm p…ôm…Ē wana-…õ, w…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ wi m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ.  
\v 27 W…õs…õm nw…õ o nw…õ w…Ēy…Ē w…õc…ôk maŇčk…ôl…õ nw…õ w…Ēy…Ē s…õnc m…Ē, w…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ wefi wa yi, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.  
\v 28 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēt…Ēmp…ôr wefi wa yi, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ. Y…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 29 S…õm yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ ny…õ y…õŇčs…õp d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē: Agb…õlk…õc, wer, asel k…Ē dokom…õn…õ da yi,  
\v 30 soked…ĒŇčk…õ, acakar, k…ômb…ômb…ôr…ôt, t…õgb…ôcm…Ēt…õ, k…Ē ak…ôlencen.  
\v 31 S…õm y…õf…õt yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ y…õs…õp dac…Ē, ny…õ y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ ogbuŇč…õn…õ pefi pa yi, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.  
\v 32 Paka mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē peliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ pap…Ēk…Ē pin pefi payi p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ k…ôroŇč, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ: T…Ēy…Ēn…õ ap…õp…õ, yamos, akata, al…Ēba, paka mp…õ o mp…õ andegbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē. Payaks…õ paka pap…Ēk…Ē domun, mba p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ. K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy dencep…ôr-…õ, p…ĒŇčs…Ēk oŇč.  
\v 33 P…õs…õl mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ yay…Ēk…Ē pin pefi payi p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ disr…õ ca c…ôl…Ēma k…ôroŇč, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ s…Ē, n…ôw…Ēk…ôc p…õs…õl pap…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 34 Peri mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē aloŇč…ôr domun nd…õ d…õy…õf…õ p…õs…õl pap…Ēk…Ē disr…õ m…Ē, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ s…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ pomun p…Ē-…õ, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ, peyi oŇč p…õb…õr…õ mp…õ o mp…õ disr…õ.  
\v 35 Paka mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē pefi pa pin pa yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ yay…Ēk…Ē p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ k…ôroŇč, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf…õ c…ôcom disr…õ-…õ, pal…ôs…ôr pi, p…Ēc…Ēf…õ k…ôcom pap…Ēk…Ē p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ oŇč nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 36 K…Ē pefi pa yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ pap…Ēk…Ē pin p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ôk…ôl…ômp k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē-…õ, domun dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk, mba fum w…ôk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ēwur…õ pi d…ônda d…ôromun m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ.  
\v 37 K…Ē pefi payi p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēk…Ē p…ômar pak…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē k…ôroŇč-…õ, m…õŇčgb…õn mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 38 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a ampuk m…õŇčgb…õn mam…Ēk…Ē teta k…ôdi-…õ, a pefi pa peliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ pap…Ēk…Ē p…õct…õmp…õn…õ mi k…ôroŇč-…õ, m…õŇčgb…õn mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēs…Ēk f…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 39 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…õs…õm nw…õ aŇčwos…õ nu k…ôs…Ēm m…Ē, wefi wis…ôrka, nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ wi m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.  
\v 40 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēs…Ēm s…õm ya pefi pap…Ēk…Ē, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ. Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēt…Ēmp…ôr s…Ē pefi pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ. 
\p  
\v 41 N…ôter yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ y…õf…õt f…ôp ny…õ y…õŇčs…õp d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, p…ôyikyik p…Ē, ta n…ôs…Ēm yi.  
\v 42 N…ôter yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē ny…õ yeŇčliŇč…õ kor ka yi k…ôroŇč m…Ē, k…Ē ny…õ y…ĒŇčk…Ēt…õ w…õc…ôk maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…õc…ôk wecep…ôr maŇčk…ôl…õ m…Ē, p…ôyikyik p…Ē.  
\v 43 Ta n…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk nk…õ anter m…Ē teta yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ y…õf…õt ny…õ y…õŇčs…õp m…Ē. Ta n…ôwos…õ yogbuŇč…õn…õ nu, y…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 44 MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. N…ôdey…Ēn…õ afum acempi aŇč…õ ampus'em m…Ē, bawo ina MARIKI, incemp. Ta n…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk teta yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ y…õf…õt ny…õ y…õŇčs…õp d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 45 MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ nw…õ …õnap…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira, idey…Ēn…õ Kanu konu m…Ē. N…ôy…Ēn…õ afum acempi aŇč…õ ampus'em m…Ē, bawo ina MARIKI, incemp. 
\p  
\v 46 Sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôc…ôm…õ s…õm dar…ôŇč, b…õmp, y…õŇč…õr…ôŇč ya d…ôromun f…ôp k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ ya d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp,  
\v 47 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pagb…õy s…õm yosoku k…Ē y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, s…õm ny…õ awos…õ k…ôs…Ēm k…Ē ny…õ ant…Ēwos…õ k…ôs…Ēm m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 12  
\s1 K…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ ka w…ôran k'elip k…ôkom-…õ 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p K…Ē w…ôran …õmb…õk…ôs p…ôkom wan w…ôrkun-…õ, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. ∆Üs…Ēk f…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē enden…ôŇčk w…ôka darenc Ňčof o Ňčof m…Ē.  
\v 3 Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas pak…ônc wan.  
\v 4 W…ôran w…ôkak…Ē p…ôyi s…Ē mata w…ôco maas k…Ē maas (33) k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ mecir m…Ēn. Ta p…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ paka mp…õ o mp…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, ta w…ôkayi s…Ē p…ôk…Ē nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku, haŇč p…ôlip k…ôlas mataka m…Ēn ma k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ. 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē w…ôran oŇčkom wan w…ôran-…õ, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč mataka moluks…ôr m…õr…ôŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē enden…ôŇčk w…ôka darenc Ňčof o Ňčof m…Ē. P…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ mecir m…Ēn mata w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (66). 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôran elip mataka m…Ēn ma k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ-…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ dokomb…ôra da wan w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti wan w…ôran, p…ôk…õr…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu tekiriŇč, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin teta poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf, k…Ē antantoriya k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, t…Ēpay teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya.  
\v 7 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…õr…õ yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôtubucn…õ s…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…Ēn. K…Ē telip-…õ, w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē …ĒŇčs…Ēk k…ôloŇč k…Ēn mecir d…ôŇčkom. Sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôc…ôm…õ w…ôran dar…ôŇč nw…õ oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…ôkom wan w…ôran m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē daka nd…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēs…Ēt…Ēn…õ aŇčkesiya Ňča teren tin m…Ē, w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē p…ôl…õk m…Ēpay m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ntantoriya yowut m…õr…ôŇč, pin p…Ēy…Ēn…õ poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf, pa m…õr…ôŇč p…Ēy…Ēn…õ poloŇčn…õ pa kiciya. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…Ēn, w…ôran w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk oŇč.¬Ľ 
\c 13  
\s1 Docu da akata nd…õ d…õncal…ôrn…õ fum m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna: 
\p  
\v 2 ¬ęK…Ē fum …Ēy…Ē p…ôk…ôf…ôr-k…ôf…ôr dakata, am…Ēnc…Ē k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…ôt…õms…ôr petel…ôr mp…õ p…õŇčl…ôps…ôr k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ē docu da akata nd…õ d…õncal…ôrn…õ m…Ē, pakek…ôr…õ w…ôkayi w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, wan k…Ēn w…ôkin.  
\v 3 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ēkc…õ arunc nŇč…õ Ňčeyi k…Ē dakata m…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ c…ôfon c…Ēn ca dakata c…ôfer…õ-…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ arunc Ňč…Ēn Ňčontukm…õ Ňč…õtas akata Ňč…Ēn-…õ, arunc Ňča docu d‚Äôakata d…õcal…ôrn…õ d…Ē. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē, p…ôloku k…Ē a …Ēs…Ēk f…õ.  
\v 4 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôkayi …Ēy…Ē p…ôt…õms…ôr petel…ôr pefer mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ētukm…õ p…õtas akata Ňč…Ēn m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôfon c…Ēn ca dakata c…ôntafer…õ f…õ-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ w…ôka arunc w…ôkak…Ē afum mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 5 Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mam…õ disr…õ, arunc Ňč…Ēn Ňčencep…ôr f…õ t…Ēk…Ē …õnasak Ňči m…Ē, runc y…õsams…ôr f…õ k…Ē dakata-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ k…Ē s…Ē afum haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 6 K…Ē mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…õmb…ôp s…Ē tam…õr…ôŇč-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē, k'…õn…ôŇčk runc ny…õ y…Ēf…Ēncn…õ, y…õsams…ôr f…õ k…Ē dakata-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ …õntam k…ôloku a fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēk, am…Ēnc…Ē Ňč…Ē. W…ôkayi p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, …Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 7 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ am…Ēnc…Ē ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ēw…Ēk…ôl k…Ē dakata-…õ, t…õm nt…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ …õnalip k…ôloku k…Ē a fum w…ôsoku …Ēf…Ē m…Ē, w…ôkayi p…ômar p…ôluks…ôrn…õ k…ôk…Ēment…ôrn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ s…Ē.  
\v 8 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ē p…ôk…Ēkc…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ am…Ēnc…Ē Ňč…Ēw…Ēk…ôl k…Ē dakata-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku a w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ. Arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ d…Ē yati. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ Ňčosump…ôr fum-…õ, pakek…ôr…õ k…Ē nda w…ôloŇčn…õ.  
\v 10 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē: K…Ē akata Ňč…Ēn Ňčowur p…ôk…ôf…ôr-k…ôf…ôr p…ôfer-…õ, k…Ē p…ôk…ôf…ôr-k…ôf…ôr p…ôfer pap…Ēk…Ē p…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē c…ôfon ca dakata k…ôfer…õ-…õ, haŇč magbali mocwur p…ôk…ôf…ôr-k…ôf…ôr p…Ēn-…õ,  
\v 11 arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ Ňč…õc…ôp k…Ē dakata. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku a w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ. W…ôloŇčn…õ …Ēf…Ēs…Ēt…õn k…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ k…Ē afum teta k…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē s…Ē, bawo …Ēs…Ēk f…õ.  
\v 12 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ d…õsams…ôr k…Ē dakata, dosump…ôr akata Ňč…Ēn f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôromp haŇč d…ôw…õc…ôk, nn…Ē o nn…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ …ĒŇčm…Ēm…ôn k…Ē dis m…Ē-…õ,  
\v 13 w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ runc yosump…ôr k…Ē dis f…ôp-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku a w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēk, bawo dis d…Ēn f…ôp defer…õ. Fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 14 Mba d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ ancop k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē magbali d…ôris m…Ē, w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ.  
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē magbali-…õ, p…ôloku w…ôkayi a …Ēs…Ēk f…õ: Magbali m…Ēs…Ēk f…õ, arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ d…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē magbali m…õs…ôkp…ôr alom mefer…õ-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôk…Ē s…Ē ndena w…ôloŇčn…õ.  
\v 17 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ arunc Ňč…Ēn Ňčefer…õ s…Ē-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku a w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk. 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē ab…õc…õ Ňčowur fum, Ňčede Ňč…õtamn…õ,  
\v 19 a t…õlp…ôs oŇč, p…ôk…ôf…ôr-k…ôf…ôr pefer pede powur da ab…õc…õ Ňč…õnayi m…Ē k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…ôt…õms…ôr petel…ôr pefer peyimb…ôr…ôr p…ôl…Ēma pede powur d…ônda-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôk…Ē p…ôment…ôrn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ.  
\v 20 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē: K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ arunc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčontukm…õ Ňč…õtas akata-…õ, c…ôfon ca d…ônda c…ôfer…ôr-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku a w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ. Arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ d…Ē, nd…õ dowur d…õb…õc…õ m…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēkc…õ arunc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ēy…Ē f…õ k…ôfon k…ôfer-…õ, arunc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčontukm…õ f…õ s…Ē Ňč…õtas akata Ňč…Ēn, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ s…Ē arunc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ēf…Ēncn…õ-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ w…ôkayi afum mataka cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 22 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ docu d…Ēw…Ēk…ôl k…Ē dakata-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku a …Ēs…Ēk f…õ. Arunc Ňča docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ d…Ē.  
