\c 14  
\s2 K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka aŇč…õ docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ dosump…ôr m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: 
\p  
\v 2 ¬ęSariy…õ ns…õ s…ôc…ôm…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka aŇč…õ docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ dosump…ôr m…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…ôŇčan. Paken…õ k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ,  
\v 3 w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôwur d…ôsaŇčka sa aka Yisrayel. K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ …õn…ôŇčk docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ da fum w…ôkaw…õ d…õntamn…õ-…õ,  
\v 4 w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôsom pasump…ôr…õ w…ôkak…Ē eyi k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ m…Ē, b…õmp yosoku m…õr…ôŇč yeyi w…ôyeŇč, padeŇč…ôr k…ôt…Ēk k…ôbotu amb…Ēnc ka s…õd…ôr\f + \fr 14:4 \fqa K…ôt…Ēk ka s…õd…ôr\ft  = t…Ēk ya at…Ēf Ňča Palestin y…Ē, k…ôt…Ēk k…Ē nk…õ k…ômb…Ēt amb…Ēnc m…Ē. \f*, taf…ôc peyim, k…Ē al…õ Ňča his…Ēp\f + \fr 14:4 \fq His…Ēp\ft  = m…Ēt…Ēk ma at…Ēf Ňča Palestin m…Ē, mm…õ amb…Ēts…õ sapu k…Ē moro mosop…õ amb…Ēnc m…Ē. Wara wa mi w…Ēy…Ē c…ôfon nc…õ c…ôwur…õn…õ al…õ m…Ē. T…Ēt…Ēk p…Ē mp…õ aŇčs…Ēks…õ afum d…ôm…Ēy…Ē mokur maŇčan m…Ē.\f*.  
\v 5 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôsom, pafay ab…õmp Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ēk…Ē d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl mp…õ p…Ēy…Ē domun decempi da d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 6 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…õk ab…õmp Ňča m…õr…ôŇč Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňčeyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē k…Ē k…ôt…Ēk k…ôbotu amb…Ēnc ka s…õd…ôr, taf…ôc peyim, k…Ē al…õ Ňča his…Ēp, p…ôgb…ôt yi f…ôp nde d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl mp…õ p…Ēy…Ē mecir ma ab…õmp Ňč…Ēk…Ē afay m…Ē.  
\v 7 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr fum w…ôkak…Ē eyi k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ docu d‚Äôakata d…õcal…ôrn…õ m…Ē mecir haŇč cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, p…ôloku fum w…ôkaw…õ …Ēs…Ēk oŇč. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôsak ab…õmp Ňčeyi w…ôyeŇč, Ňč…õf…õl…ôr Ňč…Ēk…Ē d…ôkulum.  
\v 8 Fum nw…õ as…Ēk…ôs m…Ē p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôfonn…õ c…ôfon c…Ēn f…ôp, p…ôbik…õ d…ôromun. K…Ē telip-…õ, w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk, …õntam k…ôb…õr…õ d…ôsaŇčka sa aka Yisrayel, mba p…ôyi mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč todoru ta abal Ňč…Ēn.  
\v 9 Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, p…ôfonn…õ s…Ē c…ôfon ca d…ôris f…ôp, ca domp d…Ēn, ca kek, haŇč ca d…ôf…Ēr p…ôfonn…õ s…Ē c…ôfon c…Ēn ca d…ôris c…ôlp…ôs c…ôk…Ē. P…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôbik…õ domun, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē …Ēs…Ēk. 
\p  
\v 10 Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas, w…ôkayi p…ôl…õk Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp, k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňč…õran Ňča teren tin Ňč…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp, k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt ka k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro, k…Ē moro lit…õr dac…Ē. P…ôk…õr…õ yi w…ôloŇčn…õ.  
\v 11 W…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ eyi k…ôs…Ēk…ôs fum m…Ē, p…ôc…ômb…ôr w…ôkayi k…Ē yoloŇčn…õn…õ y…Ēn MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.  
