\v 6 Aruna p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ tura tetek toloŇčn…õ, p…ôloŇčn…õ pi teta kiciya ka nk…Ēns…ôrka, p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ kiciya k…Ēn k…Ē ka aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 7 Aruna p…ôl…õk mbiyofo ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč, p…ôkek…ôr…õ yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.  
\v 8 Aruna p…ôkot yampuŇčpuŇč nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôc…ôr…õ a mbiyofo yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, Ňč…Ēk…Ē aloŇčn…õn…õ MARIKI m…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…Ēk…Ē aŇčkek…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēsak y…õŇč…ôn nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 9 Ambiyofo nŇč…õ yampuŇčpuŇč y…Ēs…ĒŇč MARIKI m…Ē, Aruna p…ôl…õk Ňči, p…ôloŇčn…õ teta kiciya.  
\v 10 K…Ē ambiyofo nŇč…õ yampuŇčpuŇč y…Ēs…ĒŇč k…ôk…Ēsak y…õŇč…ôn nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, Aruna p…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňči Ňčeyi w…ôyeŇč nde daŇčgbancan MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs Ňči kiciya a padekek…ôr…õ Ňči k…ôk…Ēsak y…õŇč…ôn nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ. 
\p  
\v 11 Aruna nk…Ēn p…ôkek…ôr…õ tura pa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya ka nk…Ēns…ôrka, p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ kiciya k…Ēn, k…Ē ka aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ. P…ôfay tura pa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya ka nk…Ēns…ôrka. Pasu t…Ēb…Ēl, mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õb…õr…õ pi disr…õ.  
\v 12 Aruna p…ôl…õk nde tetek toloŇčn…õ pa d…ôt…Ēks…Ē k…ôroŇč tap t…õlar…õ meken MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, k…Ē suray s…ôt…Ēt aŇčkulma k…ôm…õr…ôŇč, p…ôkek…ôr…õ yi k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ tadar…ôŇč, nde d…ôt…Ēks…Ē tosoku,  
\v 13 p…ôc…Ēf suray sas…Ēk…Ē MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ kinim…õ ka suray kaŇčk…Ē k…ôgb…ôp…ôrn…õ af…õŇčk nŇč…õ Ňčeyi kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Aruna k…ôt…Ēfi m…Ē.  
\v 14 Aruna p…ôgb…ôt t…õl…ôr t…Ēn d…ômecir ma tura pa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. P…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr s…Ē haŇč cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya tekiriŇč.  
\v 15 K…Ē telip-…õ, Aruna p…ôwur s…Ē p…ôfay ambiyofo Ňča k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya ka aka Yisrayel. Pasu t…Ēb…Ēl mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õb…õr…õ pi disr…õ. Aruna p…ôkek…ôr…õ mecir mam…Ēk…Ē nde k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ tadar…ôŇč. Aruna p…ôy…Ē s…Ē mecir ma ambiyofo mam…Ēk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē mecir ma tura m…Ē, p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr mecir mam…Ēk…Ē af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k…ôroŇč k…Ē tekiriŇč.  
\v 16 Ti disr…õ Aruna p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka t…Ēks…Ē tosoku, d…õtaŇči l…ôŇč…ôs da aka Yisrayel k…Ē kiciya k…ôŇčan f…ôp. K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ day-…õ, p…ôy…Ē s…Ē tin tayi aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu nŇč…õ Ňčeyi Ňča dac…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…ôŇčan disr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 17 Ali fum …Ēf…Ēyi aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ k…Ē Aruna endeb…õr…õ d…ôt…Ēks…Ē k…ôk…Ētubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs kiciya-…õ, haŇč t…õm nt…õ endewur m…Ē. Aruna p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ kiciya k…Ēn, ka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ, k…Ē ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp.  
\v 18 K'elip-…õ, p…ôwur ntende d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ p…Ēk…Ē peyi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs pi k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, p…ôl…õk mecir ma tura k…Ē ma ambiyofo, p…ôsop…ôt mi l…õn maŇčk…ôl…õ ya moŇčkubut ma tetek toloŇčn…õ.  
\v 19 Aruna p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr…õ t…õl…ôr t…Ēn mecir haŇč cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč. Kiciya ka aka Yisrayel k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ pi k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, mba ti disr…õ Aruna p…ôs…Ēk…ôs pi, poluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ paka popus. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Aruna elip k…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk ka t…Ēks…Ē, ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu k…Ē ka tetek toloŇčn…õ-…õ, pak…õr…õ k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčeyi w…ôyeŇč.  
\v 21 Aruna p…ôdeŇč…ôr waca w…Ēn m…õr…ôŇč ambiyofo ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčeyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē, p…ôl…Ēm…ôr Ňči kiciya ka aka Yisrayel, d…õtaŇči daŇčan l…ôŇč…ôs k…Ē mes maŇčan m…õl…õc f…ôp, p…ôsars…ôr Ňči. K…Ē telip-…õ, pawur…õ fum Ňča dac…Ē, p…ôkek…ôr…õ ambiyofo ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.  
\v 22 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, ambiyofo Ňč…õsar…õ kiciya ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp, Ňčekek…ôr…õ ki k…ôfo k…ôyer-yer nk…õ ant…Ēb…ôp m…Ē. W…ôkayi p…ôkek…ôr…õ ambiyofo p…ôsak Ňči nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ. 
\p  
\v 23 Aruna p…ôluks…ôrn…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, p…ôwur…õ yamos ya k…ôloto ka suwa y…Ēk…Ē …õnab…õrn…õ a k'…õmb…õr…õ nde d…ôt…Ēks…Ē tosoku m…Ē, p…ôboc yi d…ôndo deŇčgbip.  
\v 24 P…ôbik…õ d…ôndo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē ampus…õ k…Ē k…ôbik…õ m…Ē, p…ôb…õrn…õ yamos y…Ēn. Aruna p…ôwur, p…ôloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf p…Ēn k…Ē pa aka Yisrayel. P…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ kiciya k…Ēn k…Ē ka aka Yisrayel.  
\v 25 P…ôc…Ēf…õ MARIKI tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč moro ma p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ pa kiciya. 
\p  
\v 26 Fum nw…õ eŇčkek…ôr…õ ambiyofo ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…ôk…Ēsak y…õŇč…ôn nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôbik…õn…õn…õ domun a p…ôdeb…õr…õ d…ôsaŇčka.  
\v 27 Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ tura k…Ē ambiyofo ny…õ aloŇčn…õn…õ kiciya, a k'aŇčkek…ôr…õ mecir ma yi d…ôt…Ēks…Ē k…ôk…Ētubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē ka kiciya f…ôp m…Ē, pakek…ôr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč saŇčka todoru, pac…Ēf akata, s…õm k…Ē yedisr…õ ya aputuk ya yi.  
\v 28 Fum nw…õ …õŇčgbal yi d…ôn…õnc m…Ē p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôbik…õ a p…ôdeb…õr…õ d…ôsaŇčka. 
\p  
\v 29 Sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē s…Ē n…ôde n…ôcy…Ē doru o doru: Tataka ta w…ôco ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôsuŇč, ali t…õb…ôc ta n…ôsump…ôr, k…ôy…õf…õ n…ôna aka Yisrayel haŇč k…ôb…ôp acik…ôra ak…Ē Ňčancep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm tepic nu dac…Ē m…Ē,  
\v 30 bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d'antubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu. N…ôndes…Ēk oŇč MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč teta kiciya konu f…ôp.  
\v 31 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē camcam dede d…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcsuŇč. N…ôde n…ôclel…ôs sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē doru o doru. 
\p  
\v 32 K…Ē Aruna encep…ôr-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ ende p…ôctubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs kiciya k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē endey…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ anab…Ēy moro teta y…õb…ôc ya d…ôKanu, pad…ôs k…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da kas k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč. P…ôde p…ôcb…õrn…õ yamos ya d…ôKanu ya k…ôloto ka suwa.  
\v 33 Nk…Ēn ende p…ôctubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka t…Ēks…Ē tosoku, aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ, p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs aloŇčn…õ k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp kiciya k…ôŇčan. 
\p  
\v 34 Sariy…õ s…Ē, ns…õ n…ônt…Ēdesak k…ôy…Ē doru o doru m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ katin k…ôren o k…ôren disr…õ, pactam k…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs aka Yisrayel f…ôp kiciya k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ 
\p K'ay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē. 
\c 17  
\ms2 Dosoku da aka Yisrayel 
\mr 17-27 
\s1 Sariy…õ ns…õ s…ôc…ôm…õ teta mecir dar…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna, awut …Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp, a nt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom: 
\p  
\v 3 K…Ē w…ôka Yisrayel …õfaŇč k…ôfay tura, aŇčkesiya k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti wir saŇčka disr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti saŇčka tadar…ôŇč,  
\v 4 ta eŇčkek…ôr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu k…ôk…ĒloŇčn…õ pi MARIKI nde d…ôkiyi d…Ēn tekiriŇč-…õ, aŇčl…Ēm w…ôkayi w…ôsar…õ kiciya teta mecir mam…Ēk…Ē oloŇč m…Ē. AŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.  
\v 5 Ti disr…õ sariy…õ saŇčs…õ s…ôndes…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôt…Ēfay s…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan d…ôkulum, mba Ňčacken…õ yi MARIKI k…ôloŇčn…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, f…Ēr ya w…ôloŇčn…õ kiriŇč. Ňäaken…õ yi MARIKI teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu.  
\v 6 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr mecir ma yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ pa MARIKI mp…õ p…ôyi d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē. P…ôc…Ēf…õ moro ma yi MARIKI, amb…Ēnc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.  
\v 7 Ti disr…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôt…Ēs…Ē k…ôcloŇčn…õ canu ca yem nc…õ c…ôwur…õn…õ mbiyofo, nc…õ Ňčayi p…ôyamayama m…Ē. Aka Yisrayel Ňčac…ôm…õ sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē dar…ôŇč doru o doru, d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp daŇčan. 
\p  
\v 8 Awa! M…ôloku Ňča s…Ē nt…õ: K…Ē w…ôka Yisrayel, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ eyi Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē, p…ôck…õr…õ poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, poloŇčn…õ p…Ēl…Ēma,  
\v 9 ta eŇčkek…ôr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu tekiriŇč k…ôk…ĒloŇčn…õ MARIKI-…õ, aŇčwur…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. 
\p  
\v 10 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka Yisrayel, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ eyi aka Yisrayel dac…Ē m…Ē, omun mecir p…ôy…Ēn…õ mm…õ o mm…õ, iŇčkaf…ôl…ôrn…õ w…ôkak…Ē omun mecir m…Ē, iwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.  
\v 11 Bawo kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka dis, d…ômecir k…ôyi. Ina MARIKI in'…õc…ômb…ôr…õ nu mi d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ is…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu m…Ē, bawo mecir m…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs kiciya. Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ, a mi m…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôyi w…ôyeŇč ka dis m…Ē.  
\v 12 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k'iloku aka Yisrayel: Ta nw…õ o nw…õ nu dac…Ē p…ômun mecir. Ta w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ o nw…õ eŇčyi nu dac…Ē m…Ē p…ômun mecir. 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē w…ôka Yisrayel w…ôl…Ēma k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ eyi nu dac…Ē m…Ē, osump…ôr d…ôkulum w…õs…õm k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, ab…õmp ny…õ awos…õ k…ôs…Ēm m…Ē, p…ôloŇč mecir ma yi d…ônt…Ēf p…ôkufun…õ mi k…ôbof.  
\v 14 Bawo kiyi w…ôyeŇč doru f…ôp, d…ômecir k…ôyi. It'ilok…õ aka Yisrayel: Ta n…ômun mecir ma paka peyi w…ôyeŇč mp…õ o mp…õ, bawo kiyi w…ôyeŇč doru f…ôp, d…ômecir k…ôyi. Nw…õ o nw…õ omun mecir ma paka peyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē fum o fum w…ôka Yisrayel k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ eyi Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē, w…ôl…Ēma …Ēs…Ēm w…õs…õm nw…õ wefi wis…ôrka, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…õs…õm w…ôl…Ēma wendif wi-…õ, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôbik…õn…õn…õ domun, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk oŇč.  
\v 16 K…Ē fum w…ôkayi …Ēnt…Ēyak yamos y…Ēn, k'embik…õn…õ f…õ s…Ē-…õ, w…ôkayi …õŇčsar…õ kiciya.¬Ľ 
\c 18  
\s1 K…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran nk…õ am…Ēn…õ m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 MARIKI oloku Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom aka Yisrayel, m…ôloku Ňča: In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, Kanu konu.  
\v 3 Ta n…ôy…Ē mes m…Ēk…Ē aŇčy…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Misira nde n…ônayi m…Ē, ta n…ôy…Ē s…Ē mes m…Ēk…Ē aŇčy…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč nde iyi k…ôkek…ôr…õ nu m…Ē. Ta n…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ēy…Ē maŇčan dar…ôŇč!  
\v 4 N…ôde n…ôcy…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sem, bawo in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 5 N…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sem k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem: M…ôna nw…õ m…ônde k…ôcc…ôm…õ mi dar…ôŇč m…Ē, m…ôŇčyin…õ mi doru. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI. 
\p  
\v 6 Ta w…ôYisrayel nw…õ o nw…õ Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ dokom m…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI. 
\p  
\v 7 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran ka wisi nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ wiri m…Ē. Iya kam …Ēf…Ē, ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 8 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē k…Ēnc…ôra kam nw…õ o nw…õ. K…ôlap…ôs ka wisi k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôkir…õ kam, w…ôpaŇčn…õ k…õr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, nw…õ n…ômpaŇčn…õ kas m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ pakom k…Ē k…ôl…Ē konu disr…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôfo k…ôcuru. 
\p  
\v 10 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē wans…Ē kam w…ôran, nw…õ wan kam w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti wan kam w…ôran oŇčkom m…Ē. K…ôlap…ôs kam k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 11 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē wan w…ôran nw…õ k…Ēnc…ôra kam oŇčkom m…Ē. Wan w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē wisi aŇčkom…õ k…Ē, w…ôkir…õ kam …Ēf…Ē. 
\p  
\v 12 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôkir…õ ka papa kam, bawo w…ôkom…õn…õ ka papa kam …Ēf…Ē. 
\p  
\v 13 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…õnc w…ôran ka iya w…ôkam, bawo w…ôkom…õn…õ ka iya w…ôkam …Ēf…Ē. 
\p  
\v 14 Ta m…ôlap…ôs w…õnc ka wisi k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn, bawo k…Ēnc…ôra kam …Ēf…Ē. 
\p  
\v 15 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran ka wan kam w…ôrkun. W…ôran ka wan kam …Ēf…Ē. Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 16 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran ka w…õnc …ôm, k…ôlap…ôs ka w…õnc …ôm k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 17 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran k…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôran. Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr s…Ē yuruya y…Ēn y…õran ny…õ o ny…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ w…ôran, akom…õn…õ …Ēn pat Ňč…Ē. Tes t…õl…õc ta k…ôbut amera t…Ē. 
\p  
\v 18 Ta m…ôn…õnc…õ w…õnc w…ôran ka w…ôran kam k…ôyi ka w…ôran kam doru f…ôp. T…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôraca k…ôyi Ňča dac…Ē. 
\p  
\v 19 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran t…õm nt…õ enden…ôŇčk w…ôka darenc bawo w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēk f…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 20 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran ka w…õnc w…ôl…Ēma afum am dac…Ē, bawo t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk. 
\p  
\v 21 Ta m…ôloŇčn…õ m…ôc…Ēf…õ wan kam w…ôkin kanu ka yem Mol…õk. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ ti-…õ, ta n…ôfulus tewe ta Kanu kam. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 22 Ta w…ôrkun p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õŇčf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran m…Ē. P…ôyikyik mp…õ MARIKI enter m…Ē p…Ē. 
\p  
\v 23 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr ali p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ o mp…õ, bawo t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk. Ali w…ôran s…Ē ta Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl. D…õyamayama d…Ēp…ĒŇč d…Ē. 
\p  
\v 24 Ta mp…õ o mp…õ yi dac…Ē p…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk bawo mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp m…õnas…ĒŇč…õ afum a t…Ēf y…Ēl…Ēma, aŇč…õ iyi k…ôb…õl…ôs nu tekiriŇč m…Ē, k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 25 At…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč yati Ňč…Ēs…Ēk f…õ s…Ē, iluks…õ k…ôway ka kiciya ka Ňči, k…Ē at…Ēf Ňč…õŇč…õnc ak…Ē Ňčanand…õ Ňči m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 26 N…ôna aka Yisrayel k…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem, ta n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcy…Ē p…ôyikyik pap…Ēk…Ē MARIKI enter m…Ē de.  
\v 27 Afum ak…Ē ŇčananuŇčk…õn…õ k…ônd…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanay…Ē Ňči p…ôyikyik f…ôp mp…õ MARIKI enter m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēf k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 28 Ti disr…õ, ta n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ ant…Ēf k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, ŇčendeŇč…õnc n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňči k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnaŇč…õnc ak…Ē ŇčananuŇčk…õn…õ Ňči k…ônd…õ m…Ē.  
\v 29 Fum o fum …Ēy…Ē p…ôyikyik pap…Ēk…Ē mp…õ o mp…õ MARIKI enter m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. 
\p  
\v 30 N…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom mem, ta n…ônde n…ôcy…Ē p…ôyikyik mp…õ MARIKI enter m…Ē, ta n…ôde n…ôcy…Ē m…Ēy…Ē meyikyik mm…õ anuŇčk…õn…õ k…ônd…õ ka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ Ňčancy…Ē, a n…ôna n…ôdeder m…Ē. Ta m…Ēy…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē medes…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.¬Ľ 
\c 19  
\s1 Nt…õ Kanu k…ôfaŇč a pab…ôc…õ ki m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp: P…ômar n…ôy…Ēn…õ afum acempi aŇč…õ ampus'em m…Ē, bawo ina MARIKI Kanu konu, incemp! 
\p  
\v 3 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ n…ôna dac…Ē p…ôlel…ôs k…õr…õ k…Ē kas, p…ôlel…ôs s…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dem da k…ôŇčes…ôm f…ôp. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 4 Ta n…ôgbaym…õ n…ôc…ôm…õ m…õr…ôŇčka mef…ôli dar…ôŇč, ta n…ôlomp…ôs s…Ē canu ca f…õc. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē n…ônde n…ôck…õr'em yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu-…õ, n…ôloŇčn'em yi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ibaŇč k…ôloŇčn…õ konu m…Ē.  
\v 6 N…ôs…Ēm daka dad…Ēk…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ n…ôŇčloŇčn'em m…Ē k…Ē d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, y…Ēk…Ē y…õnc…ôm…õ haŇč tataka ta maas m…Ē, pac…Ēf yi.  
\v 7 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …Ēs…Ēm yeri yay…Ēk…Ē tataka ta maas-…õ, yeri y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk y…Ē, if…ĒbaŇč k…ôloŇčn…õ konu kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 8 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ endi s…Ē yeri yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, …õŇčsar…õ kiciya, bawo eyik-yik…ôs paka mp…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē: AŇčwur…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē n…ônde n…ôct…õl nde ant…Ēf Ňčonu-…õ, ta n…ôdek…Ē n…ôct…õl s…ôbomp sa yokom y…Ēk…Ē yeyi ab…Ēf Ňčonu c…ôs…ôk m…Ē, ta n…ôdek…Ē s…Ē n…ôcluks…ôrn…õ k…ôcgb…õt…ôs s…ôbomp s…ôk…Ē n…ônat…Ēn…ôŇčk d…ôk…ôt…õl m…Ē.  
\v 10 Ta n…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôpim…ôs yokom ya Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn y…Ēk…Ē aŇčsak…ôs-sak…ôs Ňči darenc m…Ē, ta n…ôw…õt…ôs s…Ē c…ôb…Ēk…ôl…õ ca yi. N…ôsak…ôr…õ yi at…Ēy…Ē daka, k…Ē acik…ôra. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 11 Ta n…ôkiy…õ, ta nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôyemb…ôr w…õnc, ta m…ôy…Ē k…Ē c…ômp…ônp…ôn.  
\v 12 Ta n…ôd…õr…ôm yem disr…õ tewe tem, k…Ē m…ôy…Ē ti-…õ, m…ôfulus tewe ta Kanu kam. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 13 Ta m…ôdir w…õnc …ôm, ta m…ôkiy…õ! Ta k…ôway ka fum nw…õ …õmb…ôc'am m…Ē k…ôdir'am d…ôwaca haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk.  
\v 14 Ta m…ôtolan…õ w…ôt…Ēne p…ôl…õc, ta n…ôboc…õ s…Ē w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk paka d…Ēp…Ē mp…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēp…ôt m…Ē. M…ôment…ôr m…Ēy…Ē mam disr…õ a m…ôlel…ôs im. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu kam. 
\p  
\v 15 Ta n…ôcboc kiti p…ôt…Ēlomp disr…õ: Ta m…ôc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka, ta m…ôbaŇč…õ w…ôka daka, mba m…ôboc…õ w…õnc …ôm kiti t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē.  
\v 16 Ta n…ôfor afum anu. Ta n…ôyems…õn…õ w…õnc konu, yem ny…õ y…ĒŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ padif k…Ē m…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 17 Ta m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õl…õc ma w…õnc …ôm, ta m…ônes…ôrn…õ k…ônal k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē teyi m…Ē de! Ta m…ôdesars…ôrn…õ kiciya tet…Ēn.  
\v 18 Ta m…ôluks…õ ay…õk, ta m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ m…õt…õl…õ nn…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčayi m…Ē. M…ôb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc …ôm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ômb…Ēt…ôrn…õ m…Ē, MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 19 N…ôde n…ôcm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sem: Ta m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ y…Ēc…Ēl m…õr…ôŇč y…õc…õc…õn…õ ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ dokom din dayi m…Ē. Ta n…ôb…Ēf ab…Ēf Ňčonu y…Ēb…Ēf ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ yin yayi m…Ē. Ta n…ôb…õrn…õ yamos ny…õ an…ĒŇčk…ôl k…ôdun…õ s…ôbeŇča sa akotan k…Ē sa kent…ôler m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran w…ôcar nw…õ w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma owur…õn…õ tet…Ēn k…ôfaŇč k…ôn…õnc…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a antawurus f…õ w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē, tam…õr…ôŇč ta antasak w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē p…ôwur dacar p…ôk…Ē y…õŇč…ôn-…õ, w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē m…Ē p…ôs…ĒŇč alamali. Mba af…Ēdif Ňča, bawo w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēr…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar.  
\v 21 W…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē p…ôken…õ MARIKI aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ poloŇčn…õ pa k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya.  
\v 22 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs w…ôkayi kiciya MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč teta k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya kaŇčk…Ē …Ēy…Ē m…Ē, MARIKI …õŇčŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē kiciya kaŇčk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč n…ôlip k…ôb…Ēf ka t…Ēk yokom yedi f…ôp-…õ, n…ôcl…Ēm yokom ya t…Ēk yay…Ēk…Ē am…Ēn…õ k…ôdi haŇč meren maas, ta n…ôdi yi.  
\v 24 Yokom ya t…Ēk yay…Ēk…Ē yendek…Ēkom teren ta maŇčk…ôl…õ m…Ē f…ôp, n…ôde n…ôcpus…õ yi ina MARIKI, n…ôck…õr'em yi k…ôkorkoru disr…õ.  
\v 25 Teren ta k…ôcam…ôt, n…ôntam k…ôdi yokom yay…Ēk…Ē, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcpim yi, yendela, y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yonu. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 26 Ta n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm s…õm ny…õ mecir mayi m…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi yi m…Ē. Ta n…ôy…Ē mes ma dure, ta n…ôgbal k…ôs…ônc.  
\v 27 Ta n…ôfonn…õ c…ôfon c…ôk…ôs…ôk ca domp donu, ta m…ôfonn…õ kek c…ôs…ôk.  
\v 28 Ta n…ôpirintn…õ ca c…ôl…Ēm d…ôkata ny…õ k…ôbik…õ k…ônt…Ēnim m…Ē, ta n…ôgbes-gbesin…õ s…Ē dis teta k…ôbal ka fum w…ôfi. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 29 Ta n…ôl…ôs…ôr delel da awut anu aran k…ôc…ĒŇč…ôs Ňča k…ôcf…ônt…ôr…õ-f…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēn…õnc…õ Ňča m…Ē, ta tedes…ĒŇč…õ afum a d…Ēt…Ēf k…ôyi ka yamayama, ta tedes…ĒŇč…õ Ňčacy…Ē mes m…õl…õc ma k…ôbut amera mam…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 30 N…ôdek…Ē n…ôclel…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm dem nd…õ o nd…õ, n…ôlel…ôs s…Ē k…ôfo k…ôsoku kem. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 31 Ta n…ôs…õp k…ôlok-loku k…Ē mera ya afi. Ta n…ôt…õn k…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk tetaŇčan. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 32 M…ôde m…ôclel…ôs abeki, m…ôde m…ôcs…ĒŇč w…ôtem p…ôlel. M…ôment…ôr d…ôm…Ēy…Ē mam a m…ôlel…ôs ina Kanu kam. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 33 K…Ē w…ôcik…ôra ender p…ôyi nu dac…Ē at…Ēf Ňčonu-…õ, ta n…ôdir k…Ē.  
\v 34 N…ôsump…ôr w…ôcik…ôra kak…Ē p…ôm…Ē w…õnc konu. N…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē p…ôm…Ē n…ônas…ôrka. N…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ a n…ôna s…Ē n…ônay…Ēn…õ acik…ôra at…Ēf Ňča Misira. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\p  
\v 35 Ta n…ôy…Ē k…ôt…Ēlomp nk…õ o nk…õ d…ôyotubuc…õ yonu f…ôp.  
\v 36 N…ôy…Ē yotubc…õ y…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu nk…õ k…ônawur…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 37 N…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sem k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem f…ôp, n…ôde n…ôcc…ôm…õ s…Ē mi dar…ôŇč. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ 
\c 20  
\s1 Kiti ka mes m…õl…õc m…Ēl…Ēma 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p Fum nw…õ o nw…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ w…ôka Yisrayel haŇč acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē, …Ēs…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn w…ôkin nn…Ē kanu ka yem nk…õ aŇčwe Mol…õk m…Ē, padif w…ôkayi. Aka Yisrayel Ňčaca-cas k…Ē masar.  
\v 3 Ina s…Ē iŇčkaf…ôl…ôr w…ôkayi f…Ēr, iwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, bawo …Ēs…ĒŇč yuruya y…Ēn yin kanu ka yem nk…õ aŇčwe Mol…õk m…Ē. Ti disr…õ, …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aŇčgbip Ňčem Ňčosoku k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, k'ofulus dosoku da tewe tem.  
\v 4 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčam…õp…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…Ēr, ta Ňčandif fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn kanu ka yem nk…õ aŇčwe Mol…õk m…Ē-…õ,  
\v 5 ina MARIKI, iŇčkaf…ôl…ôr fum w…ôkayi f…Ēr k…Ē aka kor k…Ēn disr…õ, iwur…õ Ňča aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, nk…Ēn fum w…ôkak…Ē k…Ē ak…Ē ŇčampaŇčn…õ p…ôyamayama k…ôyek-yek…ôs ka kanu ka yem ka Mol…õk kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē fum …õs…õp k…ôn…ôŇčk…õn…õ k…Ē afi k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôgbal k…ôs…ônc nk…õ o nk…õ nn…Ē afi Ňčayi m…Ē, ŇčampaŇčn…õ p…ôyamayama k…ôyek-yek…ôs ka canu ca yem cac…Ēk…Ē-…õ, iŇčkaf…ôl…ôr w…ôkayi f…Ēr, iwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. 
\p  
\v 7 N…ôpusn…õ f…Ēr yem kiriŇč, n…ôy…Ēn…õ afum acempi, bawo MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu. 
\s1 M…õn…õnc…õn…õ k…Ē m…õf…ônt…ôr…õ mm…õ am…Ēn…õ m…Ē 
\p  
\v 8 N…ôde n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sem, n…ôde n…ôcc…ôm…õ s…Ē si dar…ôŇč. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, nw…õ ompus nu m…Ē, n…ôy…Ēn…õ afum acempi. 
\p  
\v 9 Nw…õ o nw…õ ontolan…õ kas k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…õr…õ p…ôl…õc m…Ē, padif k…Ē. Nk…Ēn …õsar…õ teta defi d…Ēn sona gboŇč, bawo otolan…õ akomb…ôra …Ēn p…ôl…õc. 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē fum oŇčsump…ôr dalak…Ē k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ē k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran ka w…õnc w…ôl…Ēma Ňčayi dalak…Ē-…õ, padif afum akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp. 
\p  
\v 11 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma w…ôka kas-…õ, …õlap…ôs kas, padif m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp. Ňäasar…õ s…Ē teta defi daŇčan. 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun-…õ, padif afum akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp. D…õyamayama d…Ēp…ĒŇč d…Ē: Ňäasar…õ s…Ē teta defi daŇčan. 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē w…ôrkun Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôkos w…ôrkun p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē w…ôrkun …õŇčf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran m…Ē, m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp Ňčay…Ē p…ôyikyik mp…õ MARIKI enter m…Ē, padif Ňča m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp. Ňäasar…õ s…Ē teta defi daŇčan. 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õn…õnc…õ wan w…ôran k…Ē k…õr…õ-…õ, tes t…õl…õc ta k…ôbut amera t…Ē. Pac…Ēf w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē, wan w…ôran k…Ē k…õr…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta tes ta k…ôbut amera tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôyi nu dac…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr p…Ēc…Ēl-…õ, padif w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē, padif s…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē w…ôran …õf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl-…õ, padif w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē k…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē. Ňäasar…õ s…Ē teta defi daŇčan. 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē fum …õn…õnc…õ w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn nw…õ ŇčampaŇčn…õ kas k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, nw…õ ŇčampaŇčn…õ k…õr…õ m…Ē, Ňčak…Ē haŇč Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ-…õ, t…Ēy…Ē ta malap t…Ē Ňčay…Ē, pawur…õ Ňča f…Ēr ya aw…õnc aŇča kiriŇč. Fum nw…õ …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn m…Ē, …õsar…õ kiciya k…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran nw…õ eyi k…ôn…ôŇčk w…ôka darenc m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, k…ôc…ôr…õ m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp Ňčat…ôŇčn…õ k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ t…õm nt…õ w…ôran eyi k…ôn…ôŇčk w…ôka darenc m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 19 Ta m…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…õnc w…ôran w…ôka iya kam, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôkir…õ ka papa kam, bawo k…ôlap…ôs ka akomb…ôra am k…Ē. AŇč…õ ŇčaŇčy…Ē ti m…Ē, ŇčaŇčsar…õ kiciya k…ôŇčan. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn-…õ, Ňčalap…ôs wos ka w…ôkak…Ē. Afum akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčasar…õ kiciya k…ôŇčan, ŇčaŇčfi ta Ňčay…Ē awut-…õ. 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē fum …õn…õnc…õ w…ôran ka w…õnc-…õ, t…Ēy…Ē teyikyik t…Ē. Afum akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēt…Ē awut, tam…õr…ôŇč w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē …õlap…ôs w…õnc. 
\p  
\v 22 N…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sem k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem f…ôp, n…ôde n…ôcy…Ē mi, ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ iŇčkek…ôr…õ nu k…ônd…õ m…Ē, ta at…Ēf Ňč…õŇč…õnc nu-…õ.  
\v 23 Ta n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcy…Ē m…Ēy…Ē ma afum ak…Ē iŇčk…Ēb…õl…ôs nu f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē de! Afum akak…Ē k…ôcy…Ē k…ôŇčan mes m…õl…õc mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k'inter Ňča.  
\v 24 Mba inaloku nu: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻN…ôn'endek…Ēl…õk ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan, 
\q1 ina yati endek…Ēs…ĒŇč nu Ňči, 
\q1 ant…Ēf ŇčoboŇču Ňč…Ē dal…õ k…Ē awop. 
\m MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu, in'…õgb…õy nu k…Ē afum alp…ôs aŇč…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 25 It…Ē p…ômar n…ôcgb…õy s…õm yosoku k…Ē y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk, b…õmp yosoku k…Ē y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ôyik-yik…ôsn…õ teta s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē. S…õm, b…õmp, k…Ē y…õf…õl…ôr-f…õl…ôr ny…õ yencep…õ-cep…õ nu dac…Ē m…Ē, iŇčgb…õy yi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôc…ôr…õ ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē.  
\v 26 N…ôy…Ēn…õ afum acempi apus nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, bawo ina MARIKI, incemp. IŇčgb…õy nu k…Ē afum alp…ôs aŇč…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôy…Ēn…õ akemi m…Ē.  
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma Ňčande k…ôclok-loku k…Ē afi, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti Ňčacgbal k…ôs…ônc, paca-cas Ňča masar, padif. Ňäasar…õ s…Ē teta defi daŇčan.¬Ľ 
\c 21  
\s1 Sariy…õ ns…õ s…ôy…Ēn…õ sa aloŇčn…õ m…Ē 
\s2 C…ôke c…Ē p…ômar aloŇčn…õ Ňčayi-…õ 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa: ¬ęM…ôloku awut arkun a Aruna, aloŇčn…õ: Ta w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ k…ôbel ka fum, a nt…õ w…ôkak…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Lewy m…Ē.  
\v 2 M…õn…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a fum k…Ēn pat …Ēf…Ē: K…õr…õ, kas, wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun, wan k…Ēn w…ôran, w…õnc.  
\v 3 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn w…ôt…Ēl…Ē …Ēf…Ē-…õ, aŇčwos…õ k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk tet…Ēn. W…ôkir…õ, w…ôka k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčan disr…õ …Ēf…Ē, bawo w…ôloŇčn…õ …õntas…ĒŇč f…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun k…ôl…Ē k…ôcuru disr…õ.  
\v 4 W…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka afum …Ēy…Ēn…õ, p…ômar f…õ p…ôs…ĒŇč…õn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk p…ôfulusn…õ. 
\p  
\v 5 Ta aloŇčn…õ Ňčafonn…õ s…ôbomp mofo m…Ēl…Ēma, ta Ňčafonn…õ cek c…ôs…ôk, ta Ňčagbes-gbesin…õ dis.  
\v 6 Ňäay…Ēn…õ aŇč…õ ampus…õ Kanu k…ôŇčan m…Ē, ta Ňčafulus tewe ta Kanu k…ôŇčan, bawo Ňča ŇčaŇčk…õr'em yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ ina MARIKI m…Ē, yeri ya Kanu k…ôŇčan. It…Ē p…ômar Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum acempi aŇč…õ ampus'em m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 7 Ta aloŇčn…õ Ňčacn…õnc…õ aran ayi yamayama, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôran nw…õ aŇčl…ôs…ôr k…ôfac m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôran nw…õ Ňčasak…õn…õ k…Ē wos m…Ē, bawo w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôrkun …Ēf…Ē, nw…õ ampus…õ Kanu k…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 8 M…ôna w…ôka Yisrayel nw…õ o nw…õ m…ôde m…ôclel…ôs w…ôloŇčn…õ, bawo nk…Ēn …õŇčk…õr…õ yeri ny…õ n…ôŇčs…ĒŇč ina Kanu konu m…Ē. AloŇčn…õ Ňčade Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum apus nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē, bawo ina MARIKI incemp, k'iy…õk-y…õk aka Yisrayel nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum acempi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē wan w…ôran ka w…ôloŇčn…õ ofulusn…õ p…ôyi yamayama-…õ, kas w…ôloŇčn…õ ofulus: Pac…Ēf wan w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē p…ôyi w…ôyeŇč.¬Ľ 
\s2 Sariy…õ ns…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč p…ômar p…ôc…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč m…Ē 
\p  
\v 10 ¬ęW…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka aw…õnc aŇča aloŇčn…õ: Nk…Ēn nw…õ anab…Ēy moro d…ôromp, pad…ôs k…Ē dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ, pab…õr k…Ē yamos ya d…ôKanu m…Ē, ta p…ôsaktin…õ c…ôfon, ta p…ôwal-wali yamos y…Ēn teta defi.  
\v 11 Ta w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôk…Ē defi da nw…õ o nw…õ, ta p…ôs…ĒŇč…õn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, ali t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a kas, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…õr…õ efi-…õ.  
\v 12 Ta p…ôy…õf…õ nde k…ôfo k…ôsoku, ta p…ôdefulus k…ôfo k…ôsoku ka Kanu k…Ēn, bawo k…ôb…Ēy k…Ēn moro ma d…ôKanu k…ônapus k…Ē aloŇčn…õ dac…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 13 W…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ ant…Ēl…ôs…ôr k…ôfac m…Ē.  
\v 14 Ta p…ônas…ôr w…ôc…ôbok…ôra, ta p…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ Ňčasak…õn…õ k…Ē wos m…Ē, ta p…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ ofulusn…õ p…ôyi yamayama m…Ē. P…ôl…õk w…ôran akom…õn…õ …Ēn dac…Ē nw…õ ant…Ēl…ôs…ôr k…ôfac m…Ē,  
\v 15 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôt…ĒgbuluŇč awut nde dokom daŇčan, Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum acempi, asoku p…õs m…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI mm…õ mompus Ňča y…õb…ôc yem m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s2 Dolok…ôp nd…õ d…õŇčyams…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 17 ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna: 
\p Yuruya yam f…ôp d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp, nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ē dolok…ôp d…ôris m…Ē, ta p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč ina Kanu k…Ēn peri.  
\v 18 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma d…ôris, ta p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn'em: K…ôy…õf…õ w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk, fum nw…õ …õnt…ômb…ôl…ôr m…Ē, fum nw…õ …Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp d…ôk…ôro m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, dis d…Ēn d…õl…õc…õ k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma m…Ē,  
\v 19 fum nw…õ …õnt…õp…õ k…ôca k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…ôc…ôk m…Ē,  
\v 20 fum w…ôka k…ônd…õŇčk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, fum w…ôk…ôl…ôc, fum nw…õ …Ēy…Ē t…õs…õŇčk d…ôr…Ēf…Ēr m…Ē, w…ôka yat…ôr…õ, w…ôka am…Ēnc…Ē, w…ôrkun nw…õ ant…õmp c…Ēk…ôl m…Ē.  
\v 21 Ali w…ôkin yuruya ya Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ dac…Ē nw…õ …Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē, ta p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ tetek tem toloŇčn…õ k…ôk…õr'em yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Nw…õ …Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč Kanu k…Ēn yeri.  
\v 22 Mba w…ôkayi …õntam k…ôdi yeri ya Kanu k…Ēn, yoloŇčn…õ yosoku k…Ē ny…õ ampus‚Äôem m…Ē.  
\v 23 Mba ta w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôy…Ē dolok…ôp p…ôb…ôp k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ, ta w…ôkayi p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ s…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu, bawo …Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp. Ta p…ôfulus mofo mem mosoku, ina MARIKI impus mi.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 24 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna moloku mm…õ, k…Ē awut …Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp. 
\c 22  
\s2 Sariy…õ sa k…ôdi yeri ny…õ aloŇčn…õ Kanu m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa: 
\p  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôl…Ēm…ôr Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn mes mm…õ aŇčm…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôdi yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčacpus'em m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčafulus tewe ta dosoku dem m…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 3 M…ôloku Ňča: Yuruya ya aloŇčn…õ f…ôp dac…Ē, w…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ yoloŇčn…õ yosoku ny…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, ta w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk-…õ, aŇčwur…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē y…õb…ôc yem. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 4 W…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ yuruya ya Aruna dac…Ē docu da akata d…õcal…ôrn…õ dosump…ôr k…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôkayi domun d…õcgb…ôl…ôr d…ôk…ôs…Ēt…õ d…Ēn ta p…ôy…Ēn…õ m…Ēs…Ēt…õ-…õ, ta p…ôdi yoloŇčn…õ yosoku ya MARIKI, haŇč p…ôcs…Ēk. Tin tayi t…Ē k…Ē nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk bawo oŇčgbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ w…ôfi, k…Ē nw…õ domun d‚Äôarkun dendewur,  
\v 5 k…Ē nw…õ oŇčgbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ y…õliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ y…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti fum nw…õ k…ôgbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ k…Ēn k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk ka fum w…ôkak…Ē nk…õ o nk…õ.  
\v 6 Nw…õ o nw…õ ogbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ paka p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk, w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ, ta fum w…ôkak…Ē p…ôdi yeri ya yoloŇčn…õ yosoku, m…õn…õ w…ôkayi p…ôbik…õ.  
\v 7 Dec d…Ēnck…Ēnakal…õ w…ôkayi p…ôs…Ēk oŇč, …õntam k…ôdi s…Ē yeri yosoku ya k…ôloŇčn…õ, yeri y…Ēn y…Ē.  
\v 8 Ta w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôs…Ēm w…õs…õm nw…õ ant…Ēfay m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ w…õs…õm w…Ēl…Ēma wendif m…Ē, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 9 AloŇčn…õ Ňčandem…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sa y…õb…ôc yem, ta Ňčasar…õ kiciya ka k…ôfulus yeri ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčant…Ēlel…ôs teta yeri yay…Ēk…Ē t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôfi. Ina MARIKI, in'ompus Ňča. 
\p  
\v 10 Ta nw…õ o nw…õ w…ôt…Ēy…Ēn…õ dokom da aloŇčn…õ p…ôdi yeri yosoku ya k…ôloŇčn…õ. K…ôy…õf…õ w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr k…ôb…ôp ka w…ôb…ôc…õ ka w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč k…ôway m…Ē, ali w…ôkin ta p…ôdi yeri yosoku yay…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 11 Mba w…ôcar nw…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ …õnaway…õ p…ôsam p…Ēn m…Ē, …õntam k…ôdi yi, k…Ē fum nw…õ aŇčkom k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē, Ňčantam k…ôdi yeri yopus ya k…ôloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôt…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ …õn…õnc…õ wan w…ôran w…ôka w…ôloŇčn…õ, ta w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē p…ôdi s…Ē yeri yosoku ya k…ôloŇčn…õ.  
\v 13 Wan w…ôran ka w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēkom a wos p…ôfi, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, Ňčasak…õn…õ k…Ē wos, p…ôlukus p…ôde p…ônd…õ k…ôl…Ē ka kas p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnayi di nt…õ …õnat…Ēl…Ē m…Ē, …õntam k…ôdi s…Ē yeri ya kas. Mba ta w…ôt…Ēy…Ēn…õ yuruya ya aloŇčn…õ nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôdi yeri yosoku yay…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma, k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ endi peri mp…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ p…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ pa yeri yosoku y…Ēk…Ē endi m…Ē, p…ôkaf…ôl…õ s…Ē p…ôdeŇč…ôr alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 15 Ta aloŇčn…õ Ňčafulus yoloŇčn…õ ya aka Yisrayel ny…õ Ňčande Ňčacbel…ôr yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ Ňčampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē aloŇčn…õ Ňčandi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčas…Ēk-…õ, ŇčaŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôsar…õ kiciya nk…õ p…ômar ŇčaŇčs…ĒŇč…õ alamali m…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI nw…õ ompus yoloŇčn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôy…õk-y…õk p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 18 ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp: Fum nw…õ o nw…õ w…ôka k…ôl…Ē ka Yisrayel k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm aka Yisrayel dac…Ē edeken…õ MARIKI k…ôloŇčn…õ ka poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf: T…Ēy…Ēn…õ teta k…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ o nk…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpoc…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs f…ôp,  
\v 19 k…Ē w…ôkayi …õfaŇč a ibaŇč k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ēn-…õ, p…ôloŇčn'em p…Ēc…Ēl porkun mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ tura, aŇčkesiya, ambiyofo.  
\v 20 Ta n…ôk…õr'em p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ p…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē, if…ĒbaŇč k…ôloŇčn…õ konu kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē fum endeken…õ MARIKI wana, aŇčkesiya, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti wir teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti teta k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti teta k…ôpoc…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs-…õ, iŇčwos…õ k…ôbaŇč ka k…ôloŇčn…õ kaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ē f…õ dolok…ôp-…õ.  
\v 22 Ta n…ôken…õ MARIKI p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēt…Ēn…ôŇčk, p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ ambop…ôr k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ aŇčgbinti k…ôc…ôk m…Ē, mp…õ p…ĒŇčgb…Ēt…ôl…õ-gb…Ēt…ôl…õ c…ôfon m…Ē, p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ p…Ēy…Ē yat…ôr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti amanta k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti docu da akata d…Ēl…Ēma m…Ē. Ta n…ôkek…ôr…õ pi teta k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē.  
\v 23 M…ôntam k…ôken'em k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpoc…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs: Wana, aŇčkesiya, wir nw…õ w…Ēy…Ē k…ôc…ôk k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôca k…ôb…Ēl k…ôtas k…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē, mba if…ĒbaŇč yay…Ēk…Ē teta k…ôlas ka k…ôd…õr…ôm konu.  
\v 24 Ta n…ôk…õr…õ ina MARIKI p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ ant…õmp, mp…õ amporu-poru, mp…õ awur…õ c…Ēk…ôl k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ ancopu arit m…Ē. Ta n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcy…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yonu tat…Ēk…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňčonu.  
\v 25 Ta n…ôway acik…ôra d…ôwaca y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēk…Ē aŇčgbinti dis mofo m…Ēl…Ēma m…Ē, k…ôdeloŇčn…õ ina Kanu konu. K…ôgbinti dis da p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ pi k…ôy…Ē dolok…ôp. If…ĒbaŇč pi k…ôloŇčn…õ konu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 26 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: 
\p  
\v 27 ¬ęK…ôy…õf…õ tura, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun, ambiyofo, k'aŇčkom yi-…õ, wan p…ôyi k…õr…õ d…ônt…Ēf haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. K…ôy…õf…õ oŇč tataka ta cam…ôt-maas ta p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē, iŇčwos…õ pi k…ôbaŇč teta k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 28 Ta n…ôfay p…Ēc…Ēl p…õran k…Ē wan ka pi d…Ēs…Ēk din dayi, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ wana, aŇčkesiya k…Ē wir. 
\p  
\v 29 K…Ē n…ôndeloŇčn…õ MARIKI teta k…ôyif k…Ēn barka-…õ, n…ôc…ôm…õ sariy…õ sa k…ôloŇčn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôbaŇč ki m…Ē.  
\v 30 N…ôs…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôloŇčn…õ dad…Ēk…Ē, ali pin ta n…ôsak pa d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. 
\p  
\v 31 N…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom mem, n…ôde n…ôcy…Ē mi. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 32 Ta n…ôfulus dosoku dem, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčalel…ôs dosoku dem m…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI nw…õ ompus nu m…Ē.  
\v 33 Inawur…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ide iy…Ēn…õ Kanu konu m…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ 
\c 23  
\s1 Mataka ma c…ôsata ca Yisrayel 
\s2 D…Ēs…Ēk da K…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p C…ôsata ca k…ôyek-yek…ôs MARIKI nc…õ n…ônde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp m…Ē, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku k…ônde k…ôcyi. 
\m Mataka ma c…ôsata cac…Ēk…Ē m…Ē mam…õ: 
\p  
\v 3 Mataka cam…ôt-tin ma tataka toluks…ôr disr…õ f…ôp aŇčwos…õ nu k…ôb…ôc, mba tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē d…Ē, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku k…Ē, tetem. Ali t…õb…ôc tin ta n…ôsump…ôr d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm dad…Ēk…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk delel…ôs MARIKI d…Ē nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ôndeyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 4 C…ôsata ca k…ôyek-yek…ôs MARIKI nc…õ c…Ē n…ônde n…ôcwen…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku ka aka Yisrayel t…õm nt…õ ambonc m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s2 K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif k…Ē ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa: ¬ęTataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča teren, dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, n…ôboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr\f + \fr 23:5 \fq K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr\ft  = it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôsata nk…õ m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…õnadif…ôt awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Misira, m…õsak awut a Yisrayel m…Ē. It'aŇčwen…õ k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ ¬ęk…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr.¬Ľ\f*. 
\p  
\v 6 Tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15) ta Ňčof ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin. N…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč camcam.  
\v 7 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta tataka toluks…ôr tayi, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē.  
\v 8 N…ôck…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēk…Ē anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk, mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ. Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s2 K…ôsata ka Asek Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 10 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\m K…Ē n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňčonu nŇč…õ is…ĒŇč nu m…Ē, k…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôct…õl-…õ, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcken…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ asek Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča y…õt…õl yonu y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 11 W…ôloŇčn…õ nk…Ēn …ĒŇčk…Ētubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôbaŇč yi m…Ē. W…ôloŇčn…õ ontubucn…õ Ňči k…ôs…ĒŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm.  
\v 12 D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ n…ôntubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč asek Ňča y…õt…õl yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, id…Ē n…ôken…õ MARIKI aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē teta poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf.  
\v 13 N…ôdeŇč…ôr k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn kilo cam…ôt-tin ka k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro m…Ē. N…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē w…õn lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē, n…ôc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI. K…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē, nk…õ amb…Ēnc Ňča ki Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc m…Ē.  
\v 14 N…ôf…Ēdi ali pokom pa y…õt…õl yay…Ēk…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôcom, m…õŇčgb…õn m…õn…õk…ôt, m…õŇčgb…õn mofu, ali pin ta n…ôdi, ta n…ôntaken…õ Kanu konu sek y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya y…õt…õl yonu-…õ. T…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu sariy…õ sa doru o doru, d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp donu, nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ôndeyi m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s2 K…ôsata ka K…ôt…õl 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē MARIKI osom s…Ē Musa: ¬ęK…ôy…õf…õ ka d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ n…ôŇčk…õr…õ sek ya y…õt…õl yonu ny…õ antubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm dad…Ēk…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcl…Ēm mataka moluks…ôr cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 16 N…ôde n…ôcl…Ēm mata w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt, haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm da cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôken…õ s…Ē MARIKI k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn mofu.  
\v 17 K…ôy…õf…õ nde d…ôkiyi donu, n…ôde n…ôck…õr…õ c…ôcom m…õr…ôŇč k…ôdetubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč ci MARIKI. K…ôcom o k…ôcom p…ômar palomps…õ ki k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo k…ômaas pan…ĒŇčk…ôl ki lebin pakak…ôl. C…ôcom c…Ē nc…õ aŇčlomps…õ MARIKI y…õt…õl y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 18 N…ôdeŇč…ôr k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôcom kaŇčk…Ē: Ňäkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē, tura tin, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôc…Ēf'em yi nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč n…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē w…õn wa yi. YoloŇčn…õ y…Ē ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.  
\v 19 K…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, n…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu.  
\v 20 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka c…ôcom c…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nc…õ antubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē Ňčkesiya yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč: Yeri yopus ya MARIKI y…Ē, w…ôloŇčn…õ …Ēy…Ē yi.  
\v 21 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs im, ta n…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē. T…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu sariy…õ sa doru o doru, d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp donu, nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ôndeyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē n…ônde n…ôct…õl nde ant…Ēf Ňčonu-…õ, ta n…ôde n…ôct…õl c…ôs…ôk ca c…ôb…Ēf conu, ta n…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôgb…õt…ôs ka s…ôbomp ns…õ n…ômp…ôl…ôs tadar…ôŇč tonu m…Ē, n…ôsak…ôr…õ sas…Ēk…Ē w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka k…Ē w…ôcik…ôra. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.¬Ľ 
\s2 K…ôsata ka K…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs k…Ē K…ôfula luk 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 24 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč d…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk d…õc…õm-c…õm…ôs k…Ē dofula luk. N…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku tewe tem.  
\v 25 Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē, mba n…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s2 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēp…ĒŇč da K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya 
\p  
\v 26 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: 
\p  
\v 27 ¬ęTataka ta w…ôco ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēp…ĒŇč da K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya d…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku k…Ē, teta k…ôlel…ôs im. N…ôsuŇč d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, n…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 28 Ta n…ôsump…ôr t…õb…ôc o t…õb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, bawo d…Ēs…Ēk da K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya d…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk dotubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč, Kanu konu.  
\v 29 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õd…õnc…ôs k…ôsuŇč d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.  
\v 30 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčsumpur y…õb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, ina yati iŇčm…ôl…ôk k…Ē afum …Ēn dac…Ē.  
\v 31 Ali t…õb…ôc ta n…ôsumpur d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē. Sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp, nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ôndeyi m…Ē.  
\v 32 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, n…ôsuŇč tat…Ēk…Ē ta cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof, n…ôŇčes…ôm k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēf…Ēy haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēf…Ēy.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôsata ka C…ôl…õŇčgb…õ 
\p  
\v 33 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 34 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p Tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, paboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata ka C…ôl…õŇčgb…õ, haŇč mataka cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 35 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku k…Ē, teta k…ôlel…ôs im. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē.  
\v 36 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, n…ôcken…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ andec…Ēf…õ k…Ē m…Ē. Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku k…Ē, teta k…ôlel…ôs im. N…ôk…õr…õ ina MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ andec…Ēf'em m…Ē. K…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôlp…ôs ka k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ k…Ē, ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 37 C…ôsata canc…õ c…Ē n…ôcboc teta k…ôlel…ôs ka MARIKI, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku nk…õ n…ôde n…ôck…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ ande pacc…Ēf…õ k…Ē nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu k…ôroŇč m…Ē, yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn, yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya w…õn wa yi, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar paloŇčn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ o nd…õ m…Ē.  
\v 38 YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y'ande pacdeŇč…ôr yoloŇčn…õ ya d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm f…ôp nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka yopoc…õ yonu, yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôd…õr…ôm yonu haŇč yoloŇčn…õ yopoc…õ yonu ny…õ n…ôŇčs…ĒŇč MARIKI b…ôk…ôc yosoku p…õs m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 39 Teta k…ôsata ka c…ôl…õŇčgb…õ, tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt yati ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē k…ôt…õl ka y…Ēb…Ēf yonu k…ôlip-…õ, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcboc k…ôsata ka MARIKI mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ. Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…Ē tataka ta cam…ôt-maas ta k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē, mataka meŇčes…ôm mm…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 40 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, n…ôl…õk yokom y…Ēt…Ēt ya t…Ēk yokom yonu, bat ya komp, wara wa t…Ēk y…Ēy…Ē b…Ēp…ôr k…Ē c…ôŇčk…Ēlma ca d…ôromun, n…ôwol…ôs-wol…ôs ina MARIKI Kanu konu f…Ēr kiriŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp disr…õ.  
\v 41 K…ôren o k…ôren n…ôde n…ôcboc…õ ina MARIKI k…ôsata mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňča teren o teren disr…õ. Tede t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu sariy…õ sa doru o doru, d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp.  
\v 42 Akom aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčade Ňčacyi c…ôl…õŇčgb…õ disr…õ mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč,  
\v 43 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yuruya yonu yedec…ôr…õ a inayin…õ aka Yisrayel d…ôc…ôl…õŇčgb…õ nt…õ inawur…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 44 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Musa …õnal…Ēm…ôr aka Yisrayel c…ôsata ca k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôyek-yek…ôs MARIKI. 
\c 24  
\s1 P…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp sa aŇčgbip Ňčosoku 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: 
\p  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom aka Yisrayel Ňčak…õr'am moro m…Ēt…Ēt ma olif m…Ēf…Ēc, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôlamp s…ôctam k…ômar d…Ēf…Ēy o d…Ēf…Ēy m…Ē.  
\v 3 Aruna p…ôcc…ômb…ôr p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu nde todoru ta k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa dem k'aka Yisrayel, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôcmar t…õm f…ôp MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēf…Ēy haŇč b…ôtb…ôt m…Ē. Tede t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu sariy…õ sa doru o doru, d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp delel…ôs si.  
\v 4 Aruna p…ôdek…Ē p…ôcc…ômb…ôr s…ôlamp p…õd…õt…õ pa s…ôlamp pa k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôcmar t…õm f…ôp MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē. 
\s1 C…ôcom nc…õ aloŇčn…õ MARIKI m…Ē 
\p  
\v 5 M…ôl…õk k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt, m…ôkak…ôl c…ôcom c…ôlok-lok w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, palomps…õ k…ôcom nk…õ o nk…õ k…ômbefe kilo cam…ôt-tin.  
\v 6 N…ôboc ci f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč nde am…õsa Ňča k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, c…ôgba m…õr…ôŇč. K…ôgba o k…ôgba pac…õk ki c…ôcom cam…ôt-tin.  
\v 7 K…ôgba o k…ôgba m…ôboc ki suray s…ôt…Ēt sa k…ôl…Ēl ka k…ôt…Ēk, ns…õ andec…Ēf…õ ina MARIKI d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da c…ôcom teta k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 8 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk deŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, paboc'em c…ôcom cac…Ēk…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ c…ôde c…ôcyi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč t…õm f…ôp m…Ē. D…ôc…ôcom ca aka Yisrayel n…ônde n…ôcbel…ôr ci, danapa da doru o doru d…Ē.  
\v 9 C…ôcom cac…Ēk…Ē, ca Aruna k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn c…Ē, Ňčade Ňčacs…Ēm ci k…ôfo k…ôsoku: Yede y…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča yeri yosoku ny…õ ambel…ôr yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI k…ôc…Ēf…õ k…Ē m…Ē dac…Ē. Tede t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu sariy…õ sa doru o doru.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôt…Ēr…ôs nk…õ w…ôrok nw…õ …Ēl…Ēm…ôs Kanu …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē m…Ē 
\p  
\v 10-11 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, w…ôrok w…ôYisrayel w…ôl…Ēma kas p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôMisira, pacwe k…õr…õ Selomit wan w…ôran w…ôka Dibri w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Dan. K…Ē w…ôrok nw…õ, …ĒŇčk…Ē aYisrayel dac…Ē k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyekt…ôr w…ôka Yisrayel w…ôl…Ēma k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ d…ôndo d…ôsaŇčka. K…Ē w…ôrok nw…õ …Ēl…Ēm…ôs MARIKI p…ôcbonc tewe t…Ēn, k'ontolan…õ k…Ē p…ôl…õc. K'asump…ôr wan w…ôkak…Ē k'aŇčken…õ k…Ē Musa.  
\v 12 K'aŇčk…Ē pacaŇč…ôr k…Ē, packar MARIKI k…ôloku t…Ēk…Ē andey…Ē k…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:  
\v 14 ¬ęN…ôwur…õn…õ wan w…ôkaw…õ …Ēl…Ēm…ôs im m…Ē saŇčka disr…õ! AŇč…õ Ňčane k…Ē dim m…Ē f…ôp, ŇčadeŇč…ôr k…Ē waca d…ôromp, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ afum f…ôp Ňčac…ôr…õ a fum w…ôkaw…õ …õsar…õ k…ôciya m…Ē, k…Ē telip-…õ, k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčaca-cas…õ k…Ē masar.  
\v 15 Nt…õ t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p M…ôna nw…õ o nw…õ m…ôntolan…õ Kanu kam p…ôl…õc m…Ē, m…ôsar…õ kiciya kam.  
\v 16 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčf…ôr-f…ôr…ôs tewe ta MARIKI m…Ē, padif k…Ē: K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčanca-cas…õ w…ôkayi masar Ňčadif. W…ôkayi, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka Yisrayel, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra, andif w…ôkayi teta nt…õ …Ēl…Ēm…ôs tewe ta Kanu m…Ē. 
\s1 P…ôl…õc mp…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē w…õnc …ôm m…Ē, ip…Ē aŇčluks'am 
\p  
\v 17 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčsut fum p…ôdif k…Ē m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkayi.  
\v 18 Nw…õ o nw…õ osut p…Ēc…Ēl pa w…õnc p…ôdif pi m…Ē, p…ôs…ĒŇč p…Ēl…Ēma peyi w…ôyeŇč k…ôway ka p…Ēk…Ē endif m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 19 K…Ē fum ombop…ôr fum w…ôl…Ēma-…õ, pabop…ôr s…Ē w…ôkayi, p…ôm…Ē k…ôbop…ôr k…ôŇčk…Ē ombop…ôr w…õnc m…Ē:  
\v 20 K…ôway ka k…ôtepi k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôtepi, d…Ēf…Ēr d…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka d…Ēf…Ēr, desek d…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka desek. Dolok…ôp d…Ēk…Ē …ĒŇčy…Ē w…õnc m…Ē, id…Ē aŇčluks…õ k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 21 Nw…õ oŇčsut p…Ēc…Ēl p…ôdif m…Ē, p…ôluks…õ k…ôway ka pi, p…Ēc…Ēl peyi w…ôyeŇč, mba k'osut fum p…ôdif-…õ, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 22 Kiti kin kayi k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ w…ôcik…ôra k…ôb…ôp w…ôka Yisrayel: MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôt…Ēr…ôs ka w…ôrok 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē Musa oloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel, k'awur…õn…õ w…ôkak…Ē …õnatolan…õ tewe ta Kanu p…ôl…õc m…Ē, saŇčka tadar…ôŇč k'aŇčk…Ē paca-cas k…Ē masar. K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē. 
\c 25  
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôwurus ka nt…Ēf k…Ē k'afum 
\s2 Teren teŇčes…ôm ta ant…Ēf 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p K…Ē n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ iyi k…ôs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē, n…ôce ant…Ēf Ňčonu ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē ŇčeŇčes…ôm pipic, teta k…ôlel…ôs ka MARIKI.  
\v 3 Meren cam…ôt-tin disr…õ, n…ôntam k…ôcb…Ēf nde c…ôb…Ēf conu, n…ôc…õp…ôs wara wa Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn yonu, n…ôcpim yokom ya yi.  
\v 4 Mba teren ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, teren camcam ta k…ôŇčes…ôm ta ant…Ēf t…Ē, nt…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Ta m…ôb…Ēf dal…õ dam, ta m…ôc…õp…ôs Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn wam d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 5 Ta m…ôt…õl pas ya m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēk…Ē m…õnat…õmp…õn…õ k…Ē moŇčpoŇč m…Ē, ta m…ôpim s…Ē yokom ya Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn wam w…Ēk…Ē m…ônt…Ēc…õp…ôs d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. Teren teŇčes…ôm ta ant…Ēf t…Ē.  
\v 6 Ti disr…õ n…ôntam k…ôcdi yokom ny…õ ant…Ēf ŇčendepoŇč teren ta Ňči teŇčes…ôm disr…õ m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ m…ôna, k…ôk…Ē w…ôcar kam w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran, w…ôb…ôc…õ kam nw…õ m…ôŇčs…ĒŇč k…ôway m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr w…ôk…Ē eyi ndaram m…Ē.  
\v 7 Yokom yay…Ēk…Ē yendek…Ēy…Ēn…õ s…Ē yeri ya y…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē s…õm yonu y…Ēk…Ē yeyi nde at…Ēf Ňčam m…Ē teren tat…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ 
\s1 Teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ p…ôbotu 
\p  
\v 8 ¬ęN…ôde n…ôcl…Ēm meren meŇčes…ôm cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, haŇč cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…ôwon ka ti k…ôy…Ēn…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (49).  
\v 9 Tataka ta w…ôco ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…ôfula aluk cawon cawon: D…Ēs…Ēk da K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya d…Ē, n…ôfula luk at…Ēf Ňčonu f…ôp disr…õ.  
\v 10 N…ôpus…õ teren ta w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) tat…Ēk…Ē MARIKI, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôd…ôŇčk k…ôyi y…õŇč…ôn d…Ēt…Ēf aka s…ôdare sonu f…ôp. Teren tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu. Nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôluks…ôrn…õ k…ôbaŇč ant…Ēf k…Ē paka p…Ēn, p…ôk…Ē s…Ē afum …Ēn k…ôs…ôk nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 11 Teren ta w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) tat…Ēk…Ē tendey…Ēn…õ nu teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu, ta n…ôdeb…Ēf, ta n…ôdet…õl s…Ē pas y…Ēk…Ē yompoŇč dal…õ m…Ē, ta n…ôpim s…Ē Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn yonu ny…õ n…ônt…Ēc…õp…ôs d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 12 Bawo teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu teren topus. N…ôde n…ôcdi yokom ny…õ dal…õ donu d…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč dis…ôrka m…Ē.  
\v 13 K…ôren ka k…ôsata ka K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ, nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôlukus nde ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn.  
\v 14 K…Ē m…ôndecams…ôr w…õnc …ôm ant…Ēf, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti m…ôcway…ôr k…Ē paka p…Ēl…Ēm-…õ, ta nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôdir w…õnc.  
\v 15 M…ôway…ôr w…õnc …ôm, mba ta m…ôp…ôl…ôr k…ôl…Ēm ka meren m…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ ka teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õlp…ôs haŇč teren t…Ēk…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē, k…Ē meren m…õt…õl m…Ēk…Ē m…õnc…ôm…õ s…Ē a teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu k…ôcb…ôp s…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 16 T…Ēk…Ē meren mende k…ôcb…Ēl…õ m…Ē, it…Ē k…ôway k…ônde k…ôcp…õ. T…Ēk…Ē meren mende k…ôcbel…õ m…Ē, it…Ē k…ôway k…ônde k…ôctor, bawo k…ôl…Ēm ka k…ôt…õl k'ayi k…ôcams…ôr …ôm.  
\v 17 Ta fum o fum p…ôdir w…õnc, m…ônes…õ Kanu kam. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.  
\v 18 N…ôde n…ôc…ôm…õ sariy…õ sem dar…ôŇč, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ m…Ēy…Ē mem mokur, n…ôcc…ôm…õ mi dar…ôŇč, n…ôn…Ēn…õ b…ôk…ôc yoforu d…Ēt…Ēf.  
\v 19 Ant…Ēf Ňčendek…Ē Ňč…Ēcs…ĒŇč yokom ya Ňči, ny…õ n…ôndek…Ē n…ôcdi haŇč n…ôgb…ôrf…õn…õ m…Ē, n…ôn…Ēn…õ di b…ôk…ôc yoforu. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôcyifn…õ: ‚ÄĻK…Ē s…ônt…Ēb…Ēf paka, ta s…ômpim paka-…õ, ake s…ôndedi teren ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 21 Awa ina MARIKI, indetor…ôr nu k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt kem teren ta cam…ôt-tin disr…õ, indes…ĒŇč…õ ant…Ēf Ňčokom yokom ya meren maas.  
\v 22 Teren ta cam…ôt-maas, n…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôb…Ēf ka c…ôb…Ēf conu, mba k…ôren kaŇčk…Ē s…Ē, y…õt…õl yonu yokur y…Ē n…ôndi s…Ē, bawo yokom y…Ēk…Ē n…ônam…õŇčk m…Ē, yendelar nu haŇč ta n…ôntam yi k…ôlip k…ôdi teren ta cam…ôt-maas-…õ, n…ôntam k…ôkar teren ta cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ a n…ôccop k…ôdi ka yokom yofu.¬Ľ 
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôwurus nt…Ēf 
\p  
\v 23 ¬ęAf…Ēde paccam…ôs ant…Ēf telip katina: Ant…Ēf f…ôp Ňčemi Ňč…Ē, nde nderem n…ôyi decik…ôra, and…õ a Ňči k…ôr…õsna Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 24 Ti disr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ indes…ĒŇč nu m…Ē, m…õn…õ n…ôk…Ēc…ômb…ôr di sariy…õ s…ôwurus…õ ant…Ēf Ňčam nŇč…õ m…ônacams…ôr fum m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 25 K…Ē daka delip…ôr w…õnc …ôm, p…ôcams…ôr …ôm ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn tofok…ôl-…õ, w…õnc nw…õ ŇčanaŇčkan…õ k…ôl…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ dokom m…Ē, …õntam k…ôder p…ôwurus ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē w…õnc …õnacams…ôr …ôm m…Ē.  
\v 26 K…Ē fum w…ôkayi …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē w…õnc w…ôl…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ dokom nw…õ …õntam k…ôwurus ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē nk…Ēn ende p…ôs…Ēt…Ē daka nd…õ nk…Ēns…ôrka …õntam k…ôwurus…õ ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn Ňč…Ēk…Ē …õnacam…ôs m…Ē,  
\v 27 p…ôl…Ēm meren mm…õ mencep…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ …õnacam…ôs tofok…ôl pap…Ēk…Ē haŇč k…ôren nk…õ …Ēs…Ēt…Ē daka nd…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēwurus…õ pi m…Ē, p…ôl…Ēm s…Ē meren mm…õ m…õnc…ôm…õ a teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õcb…ôp m…Ē, p…ôdeŇč…ôr k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē p…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôk…Ē …õnaway m…Ē, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē …õntam k…ôluks…ôrn…õ nde ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn.  
\v 28 K…Ē w…ôkayi …Ēs…Ēt…Ē f…õ daka nd…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēwurus…õ ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn, haŇč teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õb…ôp, ant…Ēf ŇčeŇčyi w…ôk…Ē …õnaway Ňči m…Ē d…ôwaca. K…Ē teren tat…Ēk…Ē t…õmb…ôp-…õ, w…ôcam…ôs ka Ňči p…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôbaŇč ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 29 K…Ē fum …õncam…ôs k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn nk…õ k…ôyi dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč nd…õ as…Ē saŇčka haŇč k'an…ĒŇčk…ôr m…Ē, w…ôcam…ôs k…ôl…Ē …õntam k…ôwurus ki haŇč teren tin k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ …õnacam…ôs k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē. W…ôway k…ôl…Ē …õntam k…ôkar…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôwurus ka k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē haŇč teren tin.  
\v 30 K…Ē teren tin camcam tencep…ôr w…ôka k…ôl…Ē ender f…õ p…ôwurus k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn-…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôk…Ē …õnaway ki m…Ē k…Ē awut …Ēn. W…ôway ka k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē …Ēf…Ēluks…õ w…ôcam…ôs ka ki teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu de.  
\v 31 Sariy…õ sin sayi s…Ē w…Ēl…Ē wa s…ôdare s…ôf…õt k…Ē nt…Ēf, antam wi k…ôwurus p…ôm…Ē nt…õ aŇčluks…õ s…Ē wi as…ôrka k…Ē teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õmb…ôp-…õ. 
\p  
\v 32 S…ôdare sa aLewy, k…Ē w…Ēl…Ē w…Ēk…Ē w…Ēy…Ēn…õ waŇčan m…Ē, aLewy Ňča Ňčande Ňčactam k…ôwurus wi t…õm o t…õm.  
\v 33 Ali t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôLewy w…ôl…Ēma …õway k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē, oŇčluks…õ ki w…ôLewy w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôk…Ē …õnay…Ē ki m…Ē teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu, bawo w…Ēl…Ē wa s…ôdare sa aLewy gb…ôc…ôr…ôm w…Ē Ňčay…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.  
\v 34 Dal…õ d…Ēk…Ē deyi s…ôdare s…ôŇčan c…ôs…ôk m…Ē, af…Ēway di, dal…õ daŇčan d…Ē doru o doru.¬Ľ 
\s1 Sariy…õ ns…õ w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka …õŇčl…õk…ôr'am debe m…Ē 
\p  
\v 35 ¬ęK…Ē w…õnc …ôm eyi'm k…ôs…ôk daka delip…ôr k…Ē-…õ, m…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nk…Ēn s…Ē p…ôtam k…ôyi ndaram m…Ē.  
\v 36 Ta n…ôt…õn…ôr k…Ē k…ôdir nk…õ o nk…õ, m…ônes…õ Kanu kam, w…õnc …ôm …õntam k…ôyi ndaram k…Ē m…ôna.  
\v 37 M…ôb…Ēr k…Ē p…ôsam, mba ta m…ôwer k…Ē k…ôdeŇč…ôr ka t…Ēk…Ē m…ônab…Ēr k…Ē m…Ē. K…Ē m…ôb…Ēr k…Ē yeri-…õ, ta m…ôwer k…Ē k…ôdeŇč…ôr am.  
\v 38 MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu kam nk…õ k…ônawur…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…ôdes…ĒŇč nu at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē. Iy…Ēn…õ Kanu konu.¬Ľ 
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôwurus ns…õ s…ôy…Ēn…õ sa afum m…Ē 
\p  
\v 39 ¬ęK…Ē w…õnc …ôm …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka, p…ôcams…ôrn'am-…õ, ta m…ôc…ômb…ôr k…Ē y…õb…ôc ya dacar.  
\v 40 P…ôcb…ôc'am ndaram, m…ôcs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôway, p…ôm…Ē w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr. P…ôb…ôc'am haŇč teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu.  
\v 41 K…Ē teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õmb…ôp-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôwur k…ôl…Ē kam y…õŇč…ôn, nk…Ēn k…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčalukus nde kor k…ôŇčan, nde ant…Ēf Ňča akas aŇča.  
\v 42 Bawo amar…ôs em Ňč…Ē aŇč…õ iwur…õn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē. Af…Ēcam…ôs Ňča p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancam…ôs acar m…Ē.  
\v 43 Ta m…ôc…ômb…ôr w…õnc …ôm y…õb…ôc ya dacar, m…ôment…ôr a m…ôlel…ôs ina Kanu kam.  
\v 44 Afum a t…Ēf ny…õ y…õŇčk…õl nu m…Ē, n…ôntam k…ôcway…ôr Ňča acar arkun k…Ē aran.  
\v 45 N…ôndetam s…Ē k…ôcway acik…ôra ak…Ē Ňčandend…õ nu dac…Ē k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm m…Ē, afum aŇčan a d…ôcor ak…Ē aŇčkom at…Ēf Ňčonu m…Ē, akak…Ē n…ôntam k…ôc…ômb…ôr Ňča dacar.  
\v 46 N…ônde n…ôcsak…ôr…õ Ňča awut anu k…Ē n…ôna n…ôfi-…õ, Ňčay…Ēn…õ ak…ôŇčan. N…ônde n…ôcm…õŇčk Ňča, Ňčay…Ēn…õ nu acar doru o doru. Mba n…ôna aka Yisrayel, ta nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôc…ômb…ôr w…õnc y…õb…ôc ya dacar. 
\p  
\v 47 K…Ē w…õnc …ôm …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka, p…ôk…Ē p…ôcams…ôrn…õ w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ …õnd…õ nu dac…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…õnc ka w…ôcik…ôra w…ôk…Ē ŇčampaŇčn…õ kor kin m…Ē,  
\v 48 w…õnc konu …õntam k…ôwurusn…õ: AŇčwos…õ w…õnc w…ôl…Ēma k…ôwurus k…Ē.  
\v 49 K…Ē w…õnc …Ēnt…Ētam k…ôwurus k…Ē-…õ, nc…Ēk'…Ēn, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôkiya k…Ēn, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…õnc nw…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ dokom m…Ē Ňčantam k…ôwurus k…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēt…Ē daka dowurus…õn…õ, …õntam k…ôwurusn…õ nk…Ēns…ôrka.  
\v 50 W…ôkayi …ĒŇčl…Ēm k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôren nk…õ …õncam…ôsn…õ m…Ē haŇč meren mm…õ m…õnc…ôm…õ teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu k…ôb…ôp m…Ē. D…ôk…ôl…Ēm da meren mam…Ēk…Ē, antam k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôway nk…õ p…ômar p…ôs…ĒŇč m…Ē. Pal…Ēm k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčs…ĒŇč fum k…ôway ka y…õb…ôc m…Ē.  
\v 51 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…Ēs…Ēr…Ēb…Ēl…õ-…õ, w…ôkayi pawurus…õ k…Ē k…ôway k…ôŇčk…Ē …õnacams…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 52 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ-…õ, pal…Ēm meren mm…õ m…õnc…ôm…õ teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu k…ôb…ôp m…Ē, pas…ĒŇč w…ôk…Ē …õnaway k…Ē m…Ē k…ôway k…ôt…ôŇčn…õn…õ ka meren mm…õ m…õnc…ôm…õ m…Ē.  
\v 53 K…ôyi ka w…ôkayi f…ôp ndena w…ôk…Ē …õnaway k…Ē m…Ē, w…ôb…ôc …Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ p…ômar pas…ĒŇč k…ôway teren k…ôlip m…Ē, ta w…ôway k…Ēn p…ôc…ômb…ôr k…Ē y…õb…ôc ya dacar f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč.  
\v 54 K'awurus f…õ w…õnc konu towurus nt…õ o nt…õ-…õ, n…ôkar endewur dacar nk…Ēn k…Ē awut …Ēn teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu. 
\p  
\v 55 In'…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ēn…õ acar. Ab…ôc'em Ňč…Ē, in'owur…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Misira. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.¬Ľ 
\c 26  
\p  
\v 1 ¬ęTa n…ôde n…ôclomp…ôs m…õr…ôŇčka mef…ôli, ali ta n…ôde n…ôcpat t…õr…ôŇčka, ali tasar totontn…õ tin n…ôde n…ôcc…ômb…ôr, ta n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcc…ômb…ôr ali tasar p…õn…õk…ôs pin mp…õ n…ôndek…Ē n…ôctontn…õ f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.  
\v 2 N…ôdek…Ē n…ôclel…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus‚Äôem m…Ē f…ôp, n…ôlel…ôs s…Ē aŇčgbip Ňčosoku Ňčem. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yopoc…õ y…Ēt…Ēt ny…õ MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč m…Ē 
\p  
\v 3 ¬ęK…Ē n…ônc…ôm…õ sariy…õ sem dar…ôŇč, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom mem, n…ôcy…Ē mi-…õ,  
\v 4 iŇčs…ĒŇč nu w…ôcaf…ôn t…õm t…Ēn, y…Ēb…Ēf yonu yoŇčkom, k…Ē t…Ēk ya d…ôkulum yoŇčkom s…Ē yokom ya yi.  
\v 5 Awa nde ndoronu k…ôs…õp…ôr ka m…õŇčgb…õn k…ônde k…ôcwon haŇč t…õm t…Ēf…Ēc…ôs w…õn, k…Ē k…ôf…Ēc…ôs w…õn k…ôwon haŇč t…õm ta k…ôb…Ēf ka dal…õ s…Ē. N…ôde n…ôcdi yeri yonu n…ôcgb…ôrf…õn…õ, n…ôn…Ēn…õ s…Ē b…ôk…ôc yoforu nde at…Ēf Ňčonu.  
\v 6 IŇčf…Ēr…ôs at…Ēf Ňčonu, n…ônde n…ôcf…ônt…ôr…õ ali fum ta empempi nu-…õ. Indeb…õl…ôs'on at…Ēf Ňčonu s…õm ya dop y…õl…õc y…Ēk…Ē, dakma d…Ēf…Ēs…Ēcep…ôr at…Ēf Ňčonu.  
\v 7 N…ônde n…ôcb…õl…ôs ater…õn…õ anu aŇč…õ n…ônde k…ôcdift…õ sakma sonu m…Ē.  
\v 8 Afum anu k…ôcam…ôt gboŇč Ňčande Ňčacb…õl…ôs ater…õn…õ anu afum tasar tin, afum anu tasar tin (100) Ňčande Ňčacb…õl…ôs ater…õn…õ anu afum wul w…ôco (10.000), aŇč…õ n…ônde k…ôcdift…õ sakma sonu m…Ē.  
\v 9 Indecenc…õ nu k…ôro, is…ĒŇč nu dokomb…ôra, is…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôla, indelel…ôs s…Ē danapa dem k…Ē n…ôna.  
\v 10 N…ôndek…Ē n…ôcdi y…õt…õl yonu yokur haŇč n…ôwur…õ y…õlp…ôs n…ôb…õr yofu.  
\v 11 Indek…Ēc…ômb…ôr d…ôk…ôyi dem nu dac…Ē, if…Ēdeb…õr nu kumunt.  
\v 12 Indesol…õ nu, iy…Ēn…õ nu Kanu, n…ôna n…ôy…Ēn…õ afum em.  
\v 13 MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu, nk…õ k…ônawur…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē acar m…Ē. K'intepi k…ôtam ka aka Misira, k'is…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôyekti s…ôbomp.¬Ľ 
\s1 MARIKI k…ôpoc…õ p…ôl…õc 
\p  
\v 14 ¬ęMba k…Ē n…ônt…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mem, ta n…ônc…ôm…õ mosom mem f…ôp dar…ôŇč-…õ,  
\v 15 k…Ē n…ônce sariy…õ sem, n…ôf…ôn m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem, ta n…ônc…ôm…õ mosom mem dar…ôŇč, k…Ē n…ôncopu danapa dem-…õ,  
\v 16 nt…õ t'iŇčy…Ē nu: Indeb…õr nu ab…Ēc d…ôb…ôk…ôc, meleŇčki k…Ē fiba, nt…õ tendeyams…õ nu k…ôn…ôŇčk belbel, t…Ēcs…Ēm mataka monu meyi doru m…Ē. N…ônde n…ôcb…Ēf kif…ôli, ater…õn…õ anu Ňčande k…ôcdi yi.  
\v 17 Indeb…õr nu kumunt, ater…õn…õ anu Ňčande k…ôctam nu. AŇč…õ Ňčanter nu m…Ē Ňčande k…ôcyi nu k…ôroŇč, n…ôcy…õks…õ ta fum o fum …õnc…ôm…õ nu dar…ôŇč-…õ. 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp meyi ta n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im-…õ, int…Ēr…ôs nu cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč teta kiciya konu.  
\v 19 Indetepi k…ôdot banca konu, is…ĒŇč…õ w…ôcaf…ôn k…ôt…Ēder, y…Ēb…Ēf y…Ēf…Ēde yectes…õ at…Ēf Ňčonu.  
\v 20 S…Ēk…ôt sonu s…ônde k…ôcl…õc…õ kif…ôli, at…Ēf Ňčonu Ňč…Ēf…Ēs…Ēkom p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar m…Ē, t…Ēk yonu y…Ēf…Ēs…Ēkom. 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē n…ônc…ôm'em d…õb…ôk…ôc k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ, ta n…ôwos…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im-…õ, iŇčn…Ēc…ôr s…Ē k…ôsut…õ nu m…Ēt…Ēr…ôs cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč teta kiciya konu.  
\v 22 IŇčk…õr…õ nu s…õm ya dop, ny…õ yende k…ôcdif…ôr nu awut m…Ē, s…õm ny…õ yendelip k…ôdif…ôt ka y…Ēc…Ēl yonu, s…õm ny…õ yendes…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôpic…õ m…Ē. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē s…ôp…Ē sonu s…ôy…Ē yeryer. 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp meyi ta n…ôwos…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs kem kaŇčk…Ē, n…ôc…ôm'em d…õb…ôk…ôc-…õ,  
\v 24 ina s…Ē inc…ôm…õ nu d…õb…ôk…ôc, iŇčn…Ēc…ôr k…ôsut nu cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč teta kiciya konu.  
\v 25 IŇčk…õr…õ nu dakma doluks…õ ay…õk, nd…õ dendeluks…õ ay…õk Ňča danapa dem m…Ē. T…õm nt…õ n…ôŇčloŇčkan…õ s…ôdare sonu m…Ē, n…ôna dac…Ē iŇčk…õr…õ nu arom, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē amb…õr nu ater…õn…õ anu d…ôwaca.  
\v 26 K'indebaŇč…ôr nu k…ôcom-…õ, aran w…ôco Ňčande Ňčacb…õr…õn…õ k…ôc…Ēf c…ôcom p…Ēc…Ēf…õ k…ôcom pin, Ňčatubuc k…ôyer nu ci, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôcs…Ēm ci ta c…ôs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ-…õ. 
\p  
\v 27 K'iy…Ē s…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē ta n…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl im, n…ôs…Ēr…Ēc…ôm'em d…õb…ôk…ôc-…õ,  
\v 28 inc…ôm…õ nu d…õb…ôk…ôc icep…ôr…ôr, iŇčn…Ēc…ôr k…ôt…Ēr…ôs nu cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč teta kiciya konu.  
\v 29 N…ônde k…ôcs…Ēm dis da awut anu arkun k…Ē aran.  
\v 30 IŇčl…ôs…ôr mofo m…õsali monu nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, iwuŇč metek monu nde n…ônc…Ēf…õ suray canu conu ca yem m…Ē, il…õk c…ôbel ca afum anu afi, ideŇč…ôr ci c…ôbel ca m…õr…ôŇčka monu k…ôroŇč. Ab…ôk…ôc Ňčem Ňč…Ēb…Ēl…õ nu.  
\v 31 Indecek…ôli s…ôdare sonu, il…ôs…ôr mofo m…õsali monu, if…Ēs…ĒliŇč…ôrn…õ amb…Ēnc Ňča yoloŇčn…õ yonu nŇč…õ Ňčontor…õ-tor'em ab…ôk…ôc m…Ē.  
\v 32 Inas…ôrka in'endewoŇčk…ôr at…Ēf. Ater…õn…õ anu aŇč…õ Ňčandend…õ Ňči m…Ē, Ňčandesump…ôrn…õ cusu.  
\v 33 IŇčk…õr…õ nu afum aŇč…õ Ňčandew…õk…ôrn…õ nu m…Ē, isams…ôr nu afum a t…Ēf alp…ôs aŇč…õ dac…Ē. At…Ēf Ňčonu, aŇčl…ôs…ôr Ňči p…ôm…Ē t…õgb…ôr…õ, k…Ē s…ôdare sonu s…ôc…õk…ôl…õ. 
\p  
\v 34 Awa, meren mm…õ n…ôndeyi mar…ônt ndena ater…õn…õ anu m…Ē f…ôp, at…Ēf Ňčonu nŇč…õ n…ôsak Ňč…õl…õc…õ m…Ē, ŇčendeŇčes…ôm k…ôs…ôkp…õ ka t…Ēk…Ē n…ônat…Ēsak Ňči ŇčeŇčes…ôm m…Ē.  
\v 35 T…õm nt…õ Ňčendeyi Ňč…õl…õc…õ m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčendes…Ēt…Ē k…ôŇčes…ôm nk…õ Ňč…õnat…ĒŇčes…ôm nt…õ n…ônand…õ Ňči m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 36 Aw…õnc nu aŇča alp…ôs aŇč…õ Ňčandeyi nda ater…õn…õ aŇčan m…Ē, indes…ĒŇč Ňča defer f…Ēr. K…ôbor…õ-bor…õ ka ab…Ēp…ôr gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ônde k…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôy…õks…õ. Ňäande k…ôcy…õks…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ fum endey…õks…ôr dakma m…Ē, Ňčay…õks…õ haŇč Ňčak…Ē Ňčat…õmp…õn…õ, ta fum o fum …õnc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč-…õ.  
\v 37 Ňäandek…Ē ŇčacfoŇčk…ôn-foŇčk…ôn ŇčaccaŇč…ôr…õn…õ k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ater…õn…õ aŇčan Ňčanc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr…õ Ňča sakma m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč ali fum …õnc…ôm…õ f…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč. N…ôf…Ēdetam k…ôc…ôm…õ ater…õn…õ anu f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 38 D…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da ti, mar…ônt m…Ē n…ôndefi, t…Ēf Ňčocuru yemer nu.  
\v 39 D…ôt…Ēf ya ater…õn…õ anu, aw…õnc anu alp…ôs aŇč…õ andesak m…Ē, Ňčandete teta kiciya k…ôŇčan k…Ē ka atem aŇčan.¬Ľ 
\s1 Kanu k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ danapa d…Ēn 
\p  
\v 40 ¬ęMba aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēdefi k…ôt…Ēr…ôs kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ m…Ē, Ňčandec…õŇč kiciya k…ôŇčan k…Ē ka atem aŇčan, mes m…õl…õc mm…õ Ňčacy…Ē ina MARIKI, Ňčac…ôm'em s…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc.  
\v 41 Ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ a ina s…Ē, ic…ôm…õ Ňča d…õb…ôk…ôc, k'isams…ôr Ňča nde at…Ēf Ňča ater…õn…õ aŇčan. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan y…Ēt…Ēc…ôr…õ ina Kanu yendek…Ēlap…ôs Ňča teta k…ôt…Ēsump…ôr danapa dosu, Ňčawos…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs ka kiciya k…ôŇčan-…õ,  
\v 42 indec…õm-c…õmn…õ danapa dem nd…õ inasek k…Ē Yakuba, Siyaka, k…Ē Abraham m…Ē, ti tendes…ĒŇč'em oŇč k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ at…Ēf Ňčonu.  
\v 43 Ti disr…õ k…Ē Ňčandesak at…Ēf-…õ, at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčendetam k…ôŇčes…ôm. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčandewos…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs bawo Ňčawos…õ f…õ sariy…õ sem k…Ē Ňčaf…ôn m…Ēy…Ē mem mokur teta nt…õ Ňčant…Ēc…ôm…õn…õ m…Ēy…Ē mokur mem dar…ôŇč Ňčacfati s…Ē k…ôy…Ē sariy…õ sem m…Ē.  
\v 44 Ali t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē asams…ôr Ňča nda ater…õn…õ aŇčan m…Ē, if…Ēter Ňča doru o doru haŇč im…ôl…ôk Ňča de, if…Ēcopu s…Ē danapa dem k…Ē Ňča. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu k…ôŇčan.  
\v 45 ∆źy, indec…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča, teta danapa d…Ēk…Ē s…ônacaŇč…ôs k…Ē atem aŇčan m…Ē, aŇč…õ inawur…õn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē, f…Ēr ya afum a t…Ēf y…õlp…ôs ny…õ f…ôp kiriŇč, idey…Ēn…õ Ňča Kanu m…Ē. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 46 Sariy…õ saŇčs…õ, m…Ēy…Ē mokur k…Ē m…õt…ôks…õ mam…õ m…Ē MARIKI …õnac…ômb…ôr nk…Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi, k…ôsom ka Musa. 
\c 27  
\s1 Afum k…Ē daka nd…õ and…õrm…õ MARIKI m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:  
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: 
\p K…Ē fum …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč ka fum w…ôl…Ēma teta y…õb…ôc ya MARIKI-…õ, p…ômar w…ôkayi p…ôwurus…õ k…Ē p…ôsam mp…õ p…õnt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôway ka k…ôwurus…õ fum nk…õ ambonc nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē, nk…Ēn p…ôl…õk fum k…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 3 K…ôway kaŇčk…õ k…Ē n…ôndetam k…ôcwurus…õ afum aŇč…õ anas…ĒŇč MARIKI k…ôd…õr…ôm disr…õ m…Ē: 
\li1 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun nw…õ …Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco cam…ôt-tin m…Ē (60), pawurus…õ k…Ē p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) potubuc…õ pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku. 
\li1  
\v 4 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran …Ēf…Ē-…õ, p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco maas (30) p…Ē. 
\li1  
\v 5 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ wan nw…õ …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôcam…ôt haŇč w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) m…Ē, k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôrkun-…õ, p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20), 
\li1 k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran-…õ, p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco (10) p…Ē. 
\li1  
\v 6 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ wanf…õt w…ôka Ňčof Ňčin haŇč meren k…ôcam…ôt …Ēf…Ē-…õ, aŇčs…ĒŇč teta wan w…ôrkun p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč k…ôcam…ôt (5), teta wan w…ôran p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč maas (3). 
\li1  
\v 7 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôbeki w…ôka meren w…ôco cam…ôt-tin (60) haŇč p…ôcep…ôr …Ēf…Ē-…õ, aŇčs…ĒŇč…õ tet…Ēn p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15) k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun-…õ. K'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran-…õ, pas…ĒŇč p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco (10). 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôk…Ē …õnd…õr…ôm m…Ē …Ēy…Ē f…õ daka nd…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč k…ôway k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ m…Ē, pak…Ē pac…ômb…ôr w…ôkayi w…ôloŇčn…õ f…Ēr kiriŇč, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ t…Ēk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ēbonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka w…ôkayi daka a p…ôctam k…ôwer k…Ē k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē p…ômar p…ôs…ĒŇč m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ē mp…õ pentes…õ k…ôken…õ MARIKI m…Ē, mp…õ o mp…õ andeken…õ MARIKI m…Ē, papus pi.  
\v 10 Af…Ēs…ôkp…ôr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēt…Ēt, p…õl…õc. Af…Ēs…Ēs…ôkp…ôr…õ p…õl…õc, p…Ēt…Ēt. K'as…ôkp…ôr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl, p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēl…Ēma-…õ, ampus…õ MARIKI y…Ēc…Ēl yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp. 
\p  
\v 11 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk p…Ē-…õ, mp…õ ant…Ēwos…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ MARIKI m…Ē, paken…õ pi w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôm…Ēm…ôn.  
\v 12 W…ôloŇčn…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēm…Ēm…ôn d…Ēt…Ēt da p…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, d…õl…õc da p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē, a p…ôbonc…ôr w…ôkayi t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway m…Ē. K…ôway kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē afum ŇčaŇčk…Ēc…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč.  
\v 13 K…Ē w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl …õfaŇč k…ôwurus p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēn-…õ, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka pi k…Ē alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē fum ompus…õ k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn MARIKI, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôm…Ēm…ôn d…Ēt…Ēt k…Ē d…õl…õc da k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē, k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ēbonc…õ ki m…Ē, k'aŇčk…Ēc…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč.  
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôka k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē …õfaŇč k…ôwurus k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn-…õ, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka ki m…ôlm…ôl, a p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. K…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē fum …õl…õk ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn p…ôpus…õ MARIKI-…õ, defet d…Ēk…Ē …õŇčgbal…õ ab…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē d'aŇčk…Ēl…õk k…ôway ka di: P…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) k…ôway ka defet da m…õŇčgb…õn kilo masar maas (300).  
\v 17 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôcop ka teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…Ē w…ôkayi ompus…õ ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn MARIKI-…õ, tat…Ēk…Ē t'ambonc…õ k…Ē k…ôway.  
\v 18 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu tencep…ôr a k…Ē fum endepus…õ ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn MARIKI-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…Ēm meren m…Ēk…Ē m…õnc…ôm…õ a teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õcb…ôp m…Ē, p…ôbeli k…ôway ka ab…Ēf.  
\v 19 K…Ē w…ôka ab…Ēf …õfaŇč k…ôwurus ka ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn-…õ, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn nk…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. A p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ab…Ēf Ňčoluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňč…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôka ab…Ēf owurus f…õ ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn haŇč fum w…ôcuru p…ôway Ňči-…õ, w…ôka ab…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē …Ēf…Ēs…Ētam k…ôwurus Ňči.  
\v 21 K…Ē teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õmb…ôp-…õ, ab…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē ŇčoŇčluks…ôrn…õ MARIKI, aloŇčn…õ Ňčay…Ē oŇč Ňči. P…ôŇčyi t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē p…ôm…Ē nt…õ fum …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč paka MARIKI, ta …õntam s…Ē pi k…ôbaŇč m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē fum ompus…õ MARIKI ab…Ēf nŇč…õ …õnaway m…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ baf…Ē k…õ ka atem …Ēn k…ôsak k…Ē-…õ,  
\v 23 w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…Ēm meren mm…õ m…õnc…ôm…õ teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…Ēk…Ē k…ôb…ôp m…Ē, w…ôka ab…Ēf p…ôs…ĒŇč d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. Papus…õ p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē MARIKI.  
\v 24 K…Ē teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu t…õmb…ôp-…õ, ab…Ēf Ňčoluks…ôr w…ôka Ňči w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē fum nw…õ …õnal…õk Ňči k…õ ka atem …Ēn m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 25 K…ôway nk…õ o nk…õ ambonc m…Ē, k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku: Delel da p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč bin d…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôram w…ôco (10).¬Ľ 
\s1 Sariy…õ s…ôl…Ēma ns…õ s…ônc…ôm…õ fum k…Ē daka nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē 
\p  
\v 26 ¬ęAli fum ta p…ôpus…õ MARIKI wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēn, p…ôy…Ēn…õ wana, aŇčkesiya, wir, bawo awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn f…ôp, MARIKI …Ēy…Ē yi.  
\v 27 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk p…Ē-…õ, w…ôka pi p…ôwurus pi, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway nk…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. A p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. K'…Ēnt…Ēwurus pi-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ …õntam pi k…ôcams…ôr nw…õ …õŇčfaŇč pi m…Ē, k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 28 Paka mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ēy…Ēn…õ pa fum, w…ôkayi p…ôl…õk pi p…ôpus…õ MARIKI doru o doru m…Ē, af…Ēs…Ētam k…ôcam…ôs pi, af…Ēs…Ētam k…ôwurus pi, p…ôy…Ēn…õ fum, p…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl, p…ôy…Ēn…õ ab…Ēf nŇč…õ w…ôka Ňči …õl…õk k…õ m…Ē. Daka nd…õ o nd…õ ampus topus tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, daka dosoku d…Ē nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, af…Ēs…Ētam k…ôs…ôkp…ôr ti.  
\v 29 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum …Ēf…Ē nw…õ sariy…õ sa k…ôdif s…ôsumpur m…Ē, af…Ētam k…ôwurus k…Ē, m…õn…õ padif fum w…ôkayi. 
\p  
\v 30 Faril…õ fa y…Ēb…Ēf f…ôp, p…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēb…Ēf, p…ôy…Ēn…õ yokom ya t…Ēk, MARIKI …Ēy…Ē yi, daka d…Ē nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 31 K…Ē fum …õfaŇč k…ôwurus ka faril…õ f…Ēn-…õ, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka faril…õ f…Ēn, p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 32 Faril…õ fa y…Ēc…Ēl, c…ôna, Ňčkesiya, k…Ē cir f…ôp, cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ ya w…ôka y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ē, pa w…ôco, MARIKI ampus…õ pi.  
\v 33 Af…Ēt…õn k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē pentes…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…õl…õc…õ-…õ, af…Ēs…ôkp…ôr pi. K'as…ôkp…ôr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēl-…õ, y…Ēc…Ēl yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp ampus…õ yi MARIKI, af…Ēs…Ētam k…ôwurus yi.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 34 Mosom mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi.